NK014(pha)009:0: khrag 'thung khro bo'i 'chams kyi brjed byang kun bzang
NK014(pha)009:1: rnam par rtsen pa'i rol pa zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK014(pha)009:3: khrag 'thung khro bo'i 'chams kyi brjed byang kun bzang rnam par rtsen pa'i rol pa zhes bya ba /
NK014(pha)009:4: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa he ru ka'i ngo bo nyid la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:5: stong nyid mi phyed rdo rje'i do ra che //
NK014(pha)009:6: snying rje rnam pa gsum gyi gar stabs kyis //
NK014(pha)009:7: srid na rol pa'i skur ston he ru ka /
NK014(pha)009:8: bde chen sgyu ma'i gar mkhan der btud nas //
NK014(pha)009:9: rdo rje khro bo rol pa'i phyag rgya ches //
NK014(pha)009:10: rdo rje'i lus la mi phyed rgyas gdab phyir //
NK014(pha)009:11: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag bzhes ji lta bar //
NK014(pha)009:12: rdo rje gar gyi lus 'gyur 'dir gsal bya //
NK014(pha)009:13: de yang lta ba 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du rtogs shing /
NK014(pha)009:14: ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas snang spyod thams cad la lha'i phyag rgyas thebs pa /
NK014(pha)009:15: byed spyod gar gyi 'du 'phro la rang byan tshud
NK014(pha)009:16: pa'i sngags pas bskyed rim phyag rgya gar 'chams kyi
NK014(pha)009:17: spyod pa la 'bad par bya rigs pa nyid de
NK014(pha)009:18: / ci'i phyir na rdo rje'i lus kyi spyod pa
NK014(pha)009:19: la brten nas tshogs gnyis rlabs po che spel zhing
NK014(pha)009:20: / / las dang dngos grub bde blag tu sgrub
NK014(pha)009:21: pa'i thabs mchog rmad du byung ba yin pa'i rgyu
NK014(pha)009:22: / / mtshan gyis so // de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK014(pha)009:23: chos kun mnyam pa'i ngang rtogs na //
NK014(pha)009:24: bsgul zhing gsigs pa thams cad kun //
NK014(pha)009:25: phyag rgya yin par dpa' bos gsungs //
NK014(pha)009:26: rang gi lha yi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK014(pha)009:27: stangs stabs 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK014(pha)009:28: sangs rgyas nyid kyang skrag 'gyur na //
NK014(pha)009:29: dregs pa'i tshogs lta smos ci dgos //
NK014(pha)009:32: phyag rgya 'di dag bcings nas ni //
NK014(pha)009:33: stabs chen drag tu mchongs byas na //
NK014(pha)009:34: khams gsum dag las mchongs par 'gyur //
NK014(pha)009:35: gzhan yang go 'phang thams cad kun //
NK014(pha)009:38: de ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK014(pha)009:39: 'di ltar rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa bshad kyi rgyud dang /
NK014(pha)009:41: he ru ka gal po sogs rdo rje'i rigs kyi
NK014(pha)009:42: rgyud bla na med pa dag las gsungs pa nyid
NK014(pha)009:43: rgya bod kyi rig 'dzin rnams kyis bkral ba ltar
NK014(pha)009:44: lag len du bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK014(pha)009:46: dang po sa yi cho ga ste //
NK014(pha)009:47: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK014(pha)009:48: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK014(pha)009:49: zhes nub gsum gyi bya ba'i rim pas bstan pa las /
NK014(pha)009:50: 'dir nub dang po dkyil 'khor chen po'i sa chog
NK014(pha)009:51: gi skabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyang ba yan
NK014(pha)009:53: de nas sa gzhi byin gyis rlob pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:54: sa bsrung ba gnyis gar 'chams dang sbyar nas bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:55: de la thog mar sdoms ni /
NK014(pha)009:58: yum rlob gsol gdab rnam pa gnyis //
NK014(pha)009:59: bka' bsgos bgegs skrod khyad par du //
NK014(pha)009:60: dkyil 'khor lha yi stangs stabs dang //
NK014(pha)009:61: phur bu gdab pas rlob cing bsrung //
NK014(pha)009:62: rtag chad mtha' bsal bsngo shis bya //
NK014(pha)009:64: dang po chas su 'jug pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:65: rang lus la bar chad kyi bgegs kyis mi tshugs
NK014(pha)009:66: par bya ba'i ched du chas gos lus la bgo
NK014(pha)009:67: zhing phyag mtshan bzung bar bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:69: thog mar yo byad rnams byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:71: gsang sogs yo byad lnga po rnams //
NK014(pha)009:72: rig phyir ye shes ma 'dres gsal //
NK014(pha)009:73: chos nyid ye shes rol par sgom //
NK014(pha)009:75: chas gos lag cha rnams rang rang gi mdun du bkod de skyabs sems sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)009:76: sh+au nya t+aas chos thams cad stong pa nyid du sbyang /
NK014(pha)009:77: de'i ngang las skad cig gis lha'i nga rgyal bzung la /
NK014(pha)009:78: rang sems lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi cho
NK014(pha)009:79: 'phrul las khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i gos rgyan lag cha
NK014(pha)009:80: la sogs pa thams cad chos nyid ye shes kyi
NK014(pha)009:81: rol par rang snang bar bsam la /
NK014(pha)009:82: zhwa gos lcang lo sogs g.yas nas rngam zhing g.yon phyogs nas gyon /
NK014(pha)009:83: phyag mtshan pad skor gyi lag gis blangs la bzung bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)009:85: lha yi phyag rgya mi bzod cing //
NK014(pha)009:86: byer dang mkhu ldog byed pa yi //
NK014(pha)009:87: yul bdag kun la gser skyems sbyin //
NK014(pha)009:88: bden pa'i tshig gis bka' bsgo bya //
NK014(pha)009:89: zhes pas lha srin gyi zer mi ldang ba'i phyir gser skyems bsngo ste /
NK014(pha)009:90: phyag bzhes su phyi rol na gnas pa'i rol mo ba rnams kyis gser skyems /
NK014(pha)009:92: 'bru gsum gyiis 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i phung por byin gyis brlabs la /
NK014(pha)009:93: byin rlabs mchog stsol gyi rkang pa gnyis pa'i gnas su //
NK014(pha)009:94: yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams dkyil 'khor lha //
NK014(pha)009:96: sho lo ka gsum ka'i rkang pa bzhi pa'i gnas su /
NK014(pha)009:97: gser skyems 'di bzhes rnal 'byor mthu dpung bskyed //
NK014(pha)009:98: ces bsgyur bas bsngo bar mdzad do //
NK014(pha)009:100: gang dag ma smin 'gro gang la //
NK014(pha)009:101: gsang sgrogs nyes pa dor ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)009:105: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK014(pha)009:106: gang yang bdag las gzhan min dang //
NK014(pha)009:108: chos kun rang rig rang snang gi cho 'phrul du gsal bar rtogs pa na bstan bya'i yul dang /
NK014(pha)009:109: ston mkhan gyi gang zag gnyis so sor ma dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)009:110: 'di na snod min sems can gang yang med //
NK014(pha)009:111: ces pa'i tshul gyis gsang sgrogs kyi nyes pa mi 'byung na'ang /
NK014(pha)009:112: rnal 'byor pa rtogs pa'i gding ma tshud pa rnams
NK014(pha)009:113: kyis gdod nas 'gro ba ma lus pa dag pa'i
NK014(pha)009:114: 'khor lor grub par mos pas snod bcud dkyil 'khor
NK014(pha)009:115: du gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i sgo
NK014(pha)009:116: nas lus 'gyur la thun mong du gces pa'i yan
NK014(pha)009:117: lag / mgo bo la brjid chags pa /
NK014(pha)009:118: ro stod la seng chags pa /
NK014(pha)009:120: sgyid pa la ldem chags pa /
NK014(pha)009:122: rkang mgo la bde chags pa /
NK014(pha)009:123: bzhag sha la lhod chags pa /
NK014(pha)009:126: spyod pa dal la dod pa /
NK014(pha)009:127: phyag rgya g.yas su bcas pa 'grol na g.yon dang /
NK014(pha)009:128: g.yon du bcas pa 'grol na g.yas su dang /
NK014(pha)009:129: dbus su bca' 'grol la thad kar blta zhing 'gying ba ste bca' bsgyur bshig pa la mkhas pa /
NK014(pha)009:130: gzhan yang phod kha'i thang sha bcad /
NK014(pha)009:133: rim pa ji lta bar dpe bya khyung mkha' la lding ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:134: seng+ge ral pa sprug pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:135: rgya stag nags tshal du 'gying ba lta bu'i yon tan dang ldan pas /
NK014(pha)009:136: phyi rol nas spos btul zhing /
NK014(pha)009:137: rol mo chig brdeg che ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:138: chung gsum rol 'thab dang bcas pa spel mar brdungs pas bskul te /
NK014(pha)009:139: nang gi 'chams pa ba rnams slob dpon gyis sna drangs /
NK014(pha)009:143: lho pa rnams rang rang gi 'khor ji tsam yod pa'i dbus su phyogs dpon 'ong bar byas la /
NK014(pha)009:144: rim pa ma 'chol bar bsgrigs nas /
NK014(pha)009:145: rol 'gros gser skyems mjug gi sil 'bebs dang por 'chams dpon don /
NK014(pha)009:146: gnyis pa'i sil brdungs gcig la 'gyed /
NK014(pha)009:147: gsum pa'i sil brdungs nas rol 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:149: kyi don te dkyil 'khor 'bri sar slebs pa dang
NK014(pha)009:150: bskor lam la gral phreng ba ltar mnyam pas 'gro
NK014(pha)009:151: zhing / 'khor ba la nye ba na slob dpon dbus su rim gyis zhugs te /
NK014(pha)009:153: dang po dang gnyis pa song nas gsum pa nas ston par byed pa 'di ltar /
NK014(pha)009:156: rkang pa g.yas dang g.yon dang g.yas pa rnams lcags
NK014(pha)009:157: ris su 'degs 'bab kyis g.yas g.yon dbus gsum du
NK014(pha)009:158: lag rol pa'i 'gying gsig re song ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:159: bzhi pa rang gnas su 'dug pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:160: slob dpon rdor dril 'dzin cing dbus su khri'u la shar du phyogs pas bzhugs pa'i mdun du /
NK014(pha)009:161: zhabs bsil dang bzhi bsnol te rnam lnga dang sman gtor rak+ta rnams bshams /
NK014(pha)009:162: 'khor rnams rang rang gi rigs dang mthun pa'i phyogs
NK014(pha)009:163: so sor mnyam pa'i stabs kyis 'grengs te 'khod pa'i
NK014(pha)009:164: phyogs dpon bzhi'i mdun du'ang mchod pa sna lnga re
NK014(pha)009:165: slob dpon la ltos pa'i g.yon phyogs nas 'go brtsam
NK014(pha)009:166: mo // lnga pa dkyil 'khor spro ba ni /
NK014(pha)009:167: thog mar thun mong du mchod rdzas byin rlob ste /
NK014(pha)009:168: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ais sarba dra byam bi shwa d+ha ni h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)009:171: stong pa'i ngang las mchod snod pad+ma 'bar bar phyi
NK014(pha)009:172: nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas rnams dwangs shing thogs pa
NK014(pha)009:173: med pa 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam pa thams cad
NK014(pha)009:174: pa'i sgyu 'phrul gyi sprin rab 'byams su 'phro bas
NK014(pha)009:176: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)009:177: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK014(pha)009:179: a lo ke h+r+aih gan+d+he gan /
NK014(pha)009:180: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aah ba ling+ta
NK014(pha)009:181: te dz+wa ba ling+te ba la b+aa te gu h+ya
NK014(pha)009:183: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aah zhes pas rlob /
NK014(pha)009:185: rang nyid gtso bo yab yum du bskyed la gzhan
NK014(pha)009:186: sras kyi bya bas 'khor spro ba sgrub thabs ltar
NK014(pha)009:187: bya ba'am / de tsam gyi spros pa mi nus na /
NK014(pha)009:188: h'u h'u s+pha ra sam badz+ra g+han+de /
NK014(pha)009:189: s+pha ra sam badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK014(pha)009:190: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)009:191: zhes brjod pas bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa
NK014(pha)009:192: chen po badz+ra he ru ka yab yum du gyur
NK014(pha)009:193: pa la / ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK014(pha)009:194: sku gsung thugs sngags kyis byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK014(pha)009:196: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go&aham /
NK014(pha)009:197: a nu r+aa ga y+aa mi /
NK014(pha)009:198: dzahmh'u bam hoh h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)009:199: zhes brjod pas yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i sems
NK014(pha)009:200: sprin las rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum gnas
NK014(pha)009:201: yul sgo skyong dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK014(pha)009:202: thugs ka nas dbang mo rnams spros te rang rang
NK014(pha)009:203: gi gdan la rngams pa'i stabs kyis 'khod par gyur
NK014(pha)009:204: / slar yang byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis
NK014(pha)009:205: dkyil 'khor pa dang bcas pa'i dus gsum gyi mgon
NK014(pha)009:206: po sras dang bcas pa thams cad mkha' khyab tu
NK014(pha)009:210: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hohs spyan drangs pa la /
NK014(pha)009:211: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe sogs kyis kun bzang /
NK014(pha)009:212: +aa ha ra sogs kyis zhabs bsil /
NK014(pha)009:213: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au sogs kyis bzhi bsnol /
NK014(pha)009:214: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)009:215: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)009:216: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)009:217: zhes pas sman gtor rak+ta phul nas /
NK014(pha)009:219: drug pa yum byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:220: slob dpon gyis rigs bzhi'i yum gyis bskyed sngags rnams brjod pas /
NK014(pha)009:221: phyogs kyi slob ma bzhi po rigs bzhi khros pa'i rgyal mo bzhir bskyed la /
NK014(pha)009:228: bdun pa slob mas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:229: shar gyi phyogs dpon gyis bskul nas phyogs bzhi'i slob
NK014(pha)009:230: ma rnams kyis thun mong du slob dpon la kun
NK014(pha)009:233: rnga sil gyi rol mo dbyangs kyi 'gyur ba dang bcas pas /
NK014(pha)009:235: e ma rang snang dbyer med sku //
NK014(pha)009:236: rnam dag bsod nams mtshan gyis brgyan //
NK014(pha)009:237: dpe byad 'bru bkod ltas mi ngoms //
NK014(pha)009:238: sku lnga'i mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:239: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK014(pha)009:240: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK014(pha)009:241: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi mchog /
NK014(pha)009:242: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:244: e ma rdo rje sems chen po //
NK014(pha)009:245: rang rig mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'bar //
NK014(pha)009:246: mgon po yon tan bsam las 'das //
NK014(pha)009:247: rgyal mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:248: yon tan rin chen 'byung ba'i gtso //
NK014(pha)009:249: ma lus kun gyi re skong ba //
NK014(pha)009:250: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK014(pha)009:251: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:253: e ma rnam dag nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK014(pha)009:254: ci gsung sna tshogs sgra rigs mkhyen //
NK014(pha)009:255: bsam 'das brjod med rdo rje'i gsung //
NK014(pha)009:256: gsung lnga'i mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:257: rang bzhin dag pas gos pa med //
NK014(pha)009:258: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pa brnyes //
NK014(pha)009:259: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK014(pha)009:260: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:262: e ma mi mdzad mdzad pa che //
NK014(pha)009:263: ma chags chags bral 'dod chags mdzad //
NK014(pha)009:264: thams cad sgrol ba'i las po che //
NK014(pha)009:265: phrin las mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:266: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pas //
NK014(pha)009:267: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK014(pha)009:268: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK014(pha)009:269: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:270: thams cad kyis thun mong du /
NK014(pha)009:271: e ma gsang ba nam mkha'i thugs //
NK014(pha)009:272: mnyam nyid mi g.yo so sor gsal //
NK014(pha)009:273: kun rig snying po ye shes mchog /
NK014(pha)009:274: thugs lnga'i mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:275: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK014(pha)009:276: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK014(pha)009:278: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:280: brgyad pa slob dpon gyis gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:281: rdor dril 'dzin cing 'dzum mdangs kyis blta bzhin par /
NK014(pha)009:282: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi //
NK014(pha)009:283: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)009:284: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK014(pha)009:285: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyid pas //
NK014(pha)009:286: bdag cag rjes su bzung ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)009:287: sa 'di shis par byin rlob pa //
NK014(pha)009:288: bde bar gshegs pas mdzad du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:289: zhes pas mkha' khyab kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK014(pha)009:290: cad bskul te h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes pas nam
NK014(pha)009:291: mkha' gang ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku
NK014(pha)009:292: gsung thugs kyi byin bsdus nas bsgom shing spros pa'i
NK014(pha)009:293: dkyil 'khor dang bcas te rang la bstim mo //
NK014(pha)009:294: dgu pa bka' bsgo bas bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:295: slob dpon snyems pa dang bcas pas langs la sems
NK014(pha)009:296: can ma rig pa'i mun par lhungs shing bdud kyis
NK014(pha)009:297: byin gyis brlabs pa rnams la mngon par bltas nas
NK014(pha)009:298: / de rnams kyi bdud bsal bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)009:299: rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje 'jigs shing rngams pa
NK014(pha)009:300: mi bzad pa'i khro bo'i sprin spro ba'i skur gyur
NK014(pha)009:301: pa'i mig gnyis ma dang ta las nyi ma dang
NK014(pha)009:302: zla ba / mi 'bras h+aum las bskal pa'i mer 'bar bar gyur par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)009:303: 'khor rnams kyis rol sgra dang sbyar te /
NK014(pha)009:305: rdo rje lta bas chags pa ni //
NK014(pha)009:306: dag pas mig ni rab tu bgrad //
NK014(pha)009:307: ces gsungs pa ltar rang nyid rjes su chags pa'i
NK014(pha)009:308: rnam pas mig 'bur tshugs su bgrad rdo rje'i lta
NK014(pha)009:310: g.yas pa'i rdo rje gsor ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:311: g.yon dril bu gsil bzhin du /
NK014(pha)009:312: rkang pa g.yas g.yon gnyis kyis rwa btsal ba'i rdo rje phyed 'gros 'og tu 'byung ba ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:314: gnyis gnyis zhes par lag gnyis dkur mi brten par
NK014(pha)009:315: de nyid du 'gying ba tsam gyi khyad par gyis
NK014(pha)009:317: 'chad 'gyur gyi dgu brdungs dang bstun phyogs dpon bzhi
NK014(pha)009:318: yang do ra'i nang du zhugs te slob dpon gyi
NK014(pha)009:320: g.yas su nub dang byang gi phyogs dpon rnams 'khod
NK014(pha)009:321: pa'i mthar rnga thogs pa'i 'chams pa gzhan rnams kyis
NK014(pha)009:322: bskor te / sngar gyi phyed 'gros kyi mtha'i gnyis
NK014(pha)009:323: gnyis zhes pa'i rjes de ma thag par rnga steng
NK014(pha)009:324: bskor te / du bsgyur la / sbir sbram zhes
NK014(pha)009:325: pa lan gnyis kyi dzam len nas rnga dgu brdungs
NK014(pha)009:326: kyi brgyad grangs par g.yas sngon bteg gi rkang gnyis
NK014(pha)009:327: re mos su 'degs 'gying res 'then gyis rdo rje'i
NK014(pha)009:328: bskor te / du bsgyur la / rwa btsal nas / grangs dgu par g.yas pa 'deg /
NK014(pha)009:330: 'dzag gnyis la de khar sdad de //
NK014(pha)009:332: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyi ma dang //
NK014(pha)009:333: chos dang rta mchog snang mdzad kyang //
NK014(pha)009:334: bdag nyid chen po nga nyid yin //
NK014(pha)009:335: thams cad bka' las de ma 'da' //
NK014(pha)009:336: nga ni sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag /
NK014(pha)009:338: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i las byed kyis //
NK014(pha)009:339: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhan du dengs //
NK014(pha)009:340: zhes pa la bsgral mchod kyi dbyangs bkab nas /
NK014(pha)009:342: tshig rkang dang po bzhi la rkang g.yas g.yon re
NK014(pha)009:343: mos su 'degs 'gying gis rwa phyogs su bskor bas
NK014(pha)009:345: nga ni sangs rgyas man chod kyi rkang pa re
NK014(pha)009:346: re bzhin gyi 'gor rnga 'og brdung gis g.yas su
NK014(pha)009:347: dzam drag po re'i rjes rnga brang thad du bslang
NK014(pha)009:348: ste rdo rje'i mig gis lta bzhin du rkang pa
NK014(pha)009:349: g.yas g.yon 'degs 'jog spel bas g.yon bskor phyogs su
NK014(pha)009:350: phyin nas rnga g.yas su 'og brdungs che bzhi dang
NK014(pha)009:351: / g.yon du drang thad bslang ba'i chung bzhi spel
NK014(pha)009:352: ba lan gsum ldabs pa'i g.yas kyi che thog nas
NK014(pha)009:354: yang rnga steng brdungs su bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:355: rang sar dzam chung gnyis brdungs nas dgu brdungs 'dzag gnyis ma'i 'gros dang /
NK014(pha)009:356: bka' bsgo'i tshig dbyangs 'gros stabs dang bcas pa thams
NK014(pha)009:357: cad rnga steng brdungs dang rkang pa g.yas g.yon snga
NK014(pha)009:358: phyi go ldog pa tsam las gzhan sngar lta bus
NK014(pha)009:359: g.yon du dzam drag nas g.yas phyogs la phyir log
NK014(pha)009:360: tu bskor rjes / g.yon du steng brdungs che bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)009:361: g.yas su rnga drang thad kyi chung bzhi spel ba
NK014(pha)009:362: sngar lta bus g.yon gyi che thog nas drag 'bebs
NK014(pha)009:363: dang / yang rnga dgu brdungs nas 'gros dbyangs 'gro
NK014(pha)009:364: phyogs rnga stabs thams cad bka' bsgo dang po ji
NK014(pha)009:366: bzhi brdungs che chung spel ba lan gsum gyi g.yas
NK014(pha)009:367: kyi che bzhi'i thog chems brdungs drag por phab pa
NK014(pha)009:368: dang bstun king+ka ra'i chas su zhugs pa'i 'chams pa
NK014(pha)009:369: rnams glo 'bur du mchongs stabs rgyugs shar gyis don
NK014(pha)009:370: nas tsham rngams bya zhing gu gul gyis bdug /
NK014(pha)009:372: h+aum bzhi ba'i sngags drag por bzlas pas /
NK014(pha)009:373: thugs ka'i h+aum las khros pa'i khro sprin dang /
NK014(pha)009:375: rkang mthil gyi rdo rje rnams las 'bar ba'i 'od
NK014(pha)009:376: zer 'phros pas bgegs thams cad sreg bcom bskrad cing
NK014(pha)009:377: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin du brtan
NK014(pha)009:378: par mos la / slar yang g.yon brtsams kyi dzam
NK014(pha)009:379: gnyis dgu bskor 'dzag gnyis ma dang sbyar ba'i 'gros
NK014(pha)009:380: byas rjes rol mo rnams bzhag go //
NK014(pha)009:381: bcu pa dkyil 'khor lha'i stangs stabs la /
NK014(pha)009:382: gnad sdoms pas spyi'i khog 'grol ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:383: 'chams tshul dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)009:387: sngon rjes bya ba'i sbyor sdoms bshad //
NK014(pha)009:392: rnga yi sgra gdangs la ltos phyir //
NK014(pha)009:393: thog mar rnga brdungs rim pa slobs //
NK014(pha)009:394: rol 'gros g.yas g.yon mchongs stabs dang //
NK014(pha)009:396: chig rdeg che ba re re ste //
NK014(pha)009:397: de rjes skor zhing 'gying pa'i bar //
NK014(pha)009:398: chung brdungs gsum tsam rol 'thab bcas //
NK014(pha)009:399: bskyod 'gros g.yas g.yon lcags ris su //
NK014(pha)009:400: 'bebs tshe che brdeg drag por gcod //
NK014(pha)009:401: g.yab mo'ang bskyod 'gros lta bu las //
NK014(pha)009:402: 'bebs tshe cung zad chung bas gcod //
NK014(pha)009:404: sgyur ba rdzogs pa'i de ma thag /
NK014(pha)009:405: rkang g.yas mdun du 'babs pa dang //
NK014(pha)009:406: g.yas dang g.yon du g.yom 'gying la //
NK014(pha)009:407: sbram zhes che brdeg re re'o //
NK014(pha)009:408: g.yom 'gying bzhi grangs la bcug tshe //
NK014(pha)009:409: g.yas su bzhi rdzogs g.yon de phyed //
NK014(pha)009:410: che brdeg mnyam ste g.yon pa yi //
NK014(pha)009:411: gsum bzhir cung zad che dal brdeg /
NK014(pha)009:412: bzhi pad mchongs pad yangs pad la //
NK014(pha)009:413: re rer chung brdeg gsum gsum ste //
NK014(pha)009:414: dzam chung shin tu'ang chung brdeg gsum //
NK014(pha)009:415: pad dzam gnyis kyi sbram sbir sbam //
NK014(pha)009:416: gsum po rim bzhin cher bskyed brdungs //
NK014(pha)009:417: chig brdungs rol pa'i sbram la che //
NK014(pha)009:418: grangs la cung chung thengs brdungs rjes //
NK014(pha)009:419: chung ba bzhi lnga rol 'thab bcas //
NK014(pha)009:420: g.yab mo steng bar 'og gi dzam //
NK014(pha)009:421: de 'dra khyad par chung brdeg bya //
NK014(pha)009:422: pad rol bzhi grangs la 'jug tshe //
NK014(pha)009:423: rting gsig gar 'phog che brdeg dang //
NK014(pha)009:424: rol par theng ma mngon tsam gnad //
NK014(pha)009:425: so so'i phyag rgya bsgyur ba'i dus //
NK014(pha)009:426: 'cham skor dang ni dpa' bskyed nas //
NK014(pha)009:427: bzung ste spyugs pa'i bar dag dang //
NK014(pha)009:428: gdags rgyan ma gtogs 'gying chen nas //
NK014(pha)009:429: yum bar chig brdeg bzhi bzhi dang //
NK014(pha)009:430: chos dbyings thod skam gnyis lngar brdeg /
NK014(pha)009:431: steng bar 'og gsum brgyad brdeg la //
NK014(pha)009:432: mgo bo'i do shal drug brdeg ste //
NK014(pha)009:433: sbram la brdungs shing grangs rnams la //
NK014(pha)009:434: nan tsam byas nas kha 'bral ba //
NK014(pha)009:435: se 'bro zur gyi lugs yin legs //
NK014(pha)009:436: de kun tha ma'i grangs gcig por //
NK014(pha)009:437: cung zad chung brdeg gzhol len tshe //
NK014(pha)009:438: de yang sbram las cher bskyed brdungs //
NK014(pha)009:439: gzhol len ma gtogs thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)009:440: mtshams su sbram sbir sbram zhes par //
NK014(pha)009:441: dang po chung zhing che rim bskyed //
NK014(pha)009:442: 'grol bsdu gzhol stabs rnam gnyis la //
NK014(pha)009:443: sbir sbram rjes su'ang chung brdeg gcig /
NK014(pha)009:444: gzhol la dngos gzhi'i grangs rdzogs rjes //
NK014(pha)009:445: sbram zhes mtshams len de yang che //
NK014(pha)009:446: rlung dang chu yi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK014(pha)009:447: khro mo brgyad dang bam spro stob //
NK014(pha)009:448: lnga brdungs che chung spel ma ste //
NK014(pha)009:449: de yi dus su bzhi zhes par //
NK014(pha)009:450: che brdeg 'theng tsam byas na legs //
NK014(pha)009:451: rdo rje phyed 'gros brkyang spags dang //
NK014(pha)009:452: mkha' dang sa dkyil keng rus me //
NK014(pha)009:453: sgo ma bam gyi rdor 'gros dang //
NK014(pha)009:455: bzhi grangs mtha' thog che ba ste //
NK014(pha)009:456: la lar bar gyi gcig zhes par //
NK014(pha)009:457: mnyam brdeg gnyis gnyis spyir btang dus //
NK014(pha)009:458: che brdeg yin te ldem 'gros la //
NK014(pha)009:459: 'jug tshe de nyid chung brdeg bya //
NK014(pha)009:460: phra men brgyad la bzhi brdungs ni //
NK014(pha)009:461: theng ma che skad chung skad spel //
NK014(pha)009:462: 'di dang gnas ma'i rkang g.yas kyi //
NK014(pha)009:463: 'grol bsdu che skad res yin kyang //
NK014(pha)009:464: 'bring brdeg byas na mdzes zhes gsungs //
NK014(pha)009:466: rol pa dang ni sbrul nag gis //
NK014(pha)009:468: lhag ma 'khur nas rgyug pa rnams //
NK014(pha)009:469: phal cher nyis brdungs 'theng ma ste //
NK014(pha)009:470: rde'u'i g.yas g.yob g.yon g.yob kyi //
NK014(pha)009:473: che mnyam brel ba bzhi bzhi brdeg /
NK014(pha)009:474: mdor na rang rang phyag rgya rnams //
NK014(pha)009:475: sgyur dus dmigs bsal 'ga' ma gtogs //
NK014(pha)009:476: che brdeg yin te so so yi //
NK014(pha)009:478: chung brdeg des mtshon kun tu'ang //
NK014(pha)009:479: che skad chung skad 'thon pa dang //
NK014(pha)009:480: mtshams chod dal brel skabs thob byed //
NK014(pha)009:481: spyir na rol mo dal ba mdzes //
NK014(pha)009:482: zhes pa ste mtshon pa tsam mo //
NK014(pha)009:483: gnyis pa'ang 'di lta shes par bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:486: lag gnyis nang gdengs rkang g.yon dang //
NK014(pha)009:487: phyir gdengs rkang g.yas 'gro phyogs su //
NK014(pha)009:488: gsig mchongs byas rjes snga mas phyi //
NK014(pha)009:489: phyi mas nang du bskor nas 'gying //
NK014(pha)009:490: rkang pa dang mthun lag pa'ang //
NK014(pha)009:491: bsdu ba rol pa'i rnam pa can //
NK014(pha)009:493: lag gnyis g.yon phyogs kha sbub dang //
NK014(pha)009:494: g.yas phyogs gyen bstan gzhol ba yi //
NK014(pha)009:495: rol po gnyis rjes rkang g.yas g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:496: 'degs bzhag lag pa rol stabs mthar //
NK014(pha)009:497: g.yon 'degs len chung dang bstun nas //
NK014(pha)009:498: lag pa g.yon par g.yas pa yis //
NK014(pha)009:499: nang skor steng du 'phyar byed pa //
NK014(pha)009:500: 'di ni chig brdungs rol pa yin //
NK014(pha)009:501: rkang pa g.yas pas mdun du dang //
NK014(pha)009:502: g.yon pas g.yas dang g.yas pas dbus //
NK014(pha)009:503: g.yas kyis g.yon dang g.yon pa yis //
NK014(pha)009:504: dbus su yangs pad skyur ba re //
NK014(pha)009:505: rdzogs par byed pa bzhi pad do //
NK014(pha)009:506: rkang g.yas kho nas dbus dang g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:507: g.yon gyis dbus dang g.yas phyogs su //
NK014(pha)009:508: yangs pad skyur rdzogs mchongs pad yin //
NK014(pha)009:509: chung brdeg gsum la b+han phur gnyis //
NK014(pha)009:510: thugs kar mnyam nas g.yon g.yas su //
NK014(pha)009:511: gcu zhing rkang g.yon 'degs chung gis //
NK014(pha)009:512: len pa de ni dzam chung ngo //
NK014(pha)009:513: sbram sbir sbram la rkang lag g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:515: de ldog g.yon pas 'grol byed cing //
NK014(pha)009:516: dbus su pad bskor gyis bsdu ba //
NK014(pha)009:517: 'grol bsdu zhes su grags pa yin //
NK014(pha)009:519: sbram la rting gsig phur dar g.yob //
NK014(pha)009:520: sbir zhes skyur rjes sbram sbram la //
NK014(pha)009:521: g.yas phob g.yon pa 'gro phyogs su //
NK014(pha)009:522: gom gang nur nas rkang lag g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:523: gzhol nas sbir sbram la b+han skra //
NK014(pha)009:525: byed pa g.yas pa'i gzhol yin te //
NK014(pha)009:526: de ldog g.yon pa'i gzhol du grags //
NK014(pha)009:527: phur dar g.yon pa'i 'khrig ma nas //
NK014(pha)009:528: drangs te lag gnyis phyir gdengs dang //
NK014(pha)009:529: mnyam du rkang g.yas 'gro phyogs mchongs //
NK014(pha)009:530: de'i rtsar rkang g.yon grud pa'i snar //
NK014(pha)009:531: g.yas pa'i rting gtad gsig cing 'gying //
NK014(pha)009:532: bskyod 'gros zhes grags de yi tshe //
NK014(pha)009:533: lag gnyis brgyang ba mtshams chen te //
NK014(pha)009:534: dkur brten byas na mtshams chung zer //
NK014(pha)009:535: de bzhin lag gnyis dkur brten nas //
NK014(pha)009:537: chig brdungs ldem ste lag de bzhin //
NK014(pha)009:538: byas la rkang pa bzhi 'gros ltar //
NK014(pha)009:539: 'gro ba bzhi brdungs ldem du grags //
NK014(pha)009:540: bzhi pad mchongs pad 'grol bsdu dang //
NK014(pha)009:541: rol pa rnams ni bzhi brdungs dang //
NK014(pha)009:542: de bzhin lnga brdungs kyis bcings na //
NK014(pha)009:543: de dang de yi der grags mod //
NK014(pha)009:544: 'on kyang mchongs pad yongs rdzogs ni //
NK014(pha)009:545: gcig brdungs las gzhan mdzad srol med //
NK014(pha)009:546: mdor na gral rim bar thag rnams //
NK014(pha)009:547: phreng ba rgyus 'dra do ra snyoms //
NK014(pha)009:548: ha cang mi dal mi brel la //
NK014(pha)009:551: nyams kyis kun tu mdzes pa gces //
NK014(pha)009:553: gsum pa'ang 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:554: 'chams gang so so'i sngon rjes su //
NK014(pha)009:555: bzhi pad mchongs pad gzhol stabs dang //
NK014(pha)009:556: 'grol bsdu gang byed sdom tshig bshad //
NK014(pha)009:557: chos dbyings mkha' 'gro dpa' bskyed dang //
NK014(pha)009:559: steng bar 'og gsum byin gyis rlob //
NK014(pha)009:560: nam mkha' rlung dang chu dkyil dang //
NK014(pha)009:561: 'gying chen nas bzung sgo ma'i bar //
NK014(pha)009:562: bzhi pad sngon 'gro mchongs pad rjes //
NK014(pha)009:563: rdo rje brkyang ma sa dkyil dang //
NK014(pha)009:564: me dkyil bzhi pad sngo 'gro las //
NK014(pha)009:565: rjes su bzhi brdungs ldem la 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:566: keng rus gzhal yas khang gnyis kyi //
NK014(pha)009:567: sngon rjes gnyis gar mchongs pad dang //
NK014(pha)009:568: g.yab mo rdo rje phyed 'gros dang //
NK014(pha)009:570: rol pa dang ni sbrul nag gis //
NK014(pha)009:573: dgu la sngon du mchongs pad bya //
NK014(pha)009:574: rjes su rang rang bskor ba'i 'gros //
NK014(pha)009:575: spro stob sngon du bzhi pad yin //
NK014(pha)009:577: gtso bo'i g.yas g.yon bar tha'i phyag /
NK014(pha)009:578: zhabs dang do shal gos rnam gsum //
NK014(pha)009:579: khyung gshog rnams la gzhol stabs bya //
NK014(pha)009:580: steng bar 'og gsum byin rlob dang //
NK014(pha)009:582: dbu dang rtsa phyag thod skam rgyan //
NK014(pha)009:583: rtse gsum rigs bzhi'i gyad 'chams dang //
NK014(pha)009:584: yum dang khro mo phra men dang //
NK014(pha)009:586: gang zhig mthong ba brgyud pa yis //
NK014(pha)009:587: sbyangs rjes nam zhig brjed srid na //
NK014(pha)009:588: 'di tsam bltas pas dran sos nas //
NK014(pha)009:589: rtsol med thon phyir gces par bzung //
NK014(pha)009:591: gnyis pa 'chams tshul dngos bshad pa la /
NK014(pha)009:592: sngon 'gro'i stangs stabs kyis spyir rlob pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:593: dngos gzhi so so'i stangs stabs kyis bye brag tu rlob pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)009:595: 'chams skor gsum dang chos dbyings bskyed //
NK014(pha)009:596: dbang sdud mkha' 'gro dpa' bskyed dang //
NK014(pha)009:598: nam mkha' bar snang sa gzhi gsum //
NK014(pha)009:600: rdo rje phyed brkyang spags gsum gyis //
NK014(pha)009:604: sngar gyi bgegs bskrad song nas rol mo rnams bzhag rjes /
NK014(pha)009:605: thams cad b+han phur thogs te sa gzhi rnams khod
NK014(pha)009:606: snyoms par bya ba'i phyir 'chams skor lan gsum gyis
NK014(pha)009:610: chig brdungs rol pa'i rjes rkang g.yas bteg ste rol
NK014(pha)009:611: 'gros la bcug nas ji ltar rigs pa bskor mtshams
NK014(pha)009:613: zhes lag gnyis phyir gdengs te rkang g.yas g.yon gyi rtser lcags ris su bzhag nas /
NK014(pha)009:614: che brdeg bzhi la lus g.yas su bskor ba'i do
NK014(pha)009:615: ra'i rgyab tu chung gsum la yangs pad skyur gtod
NK014(pha)009:616: nas / che bzhir rkang pa lcags ris ldog pas
NK014(pha)009:617: lus g.yon du bskor ba'i chung gsum la do ra'i
NK014(pha)009:618: nang du yangs pad skyur gtod dang /
NK014(pha)009:619: rkang g.yon 'gro phyogs su phab ste rol 'gros nas /
NK014(pha)009:621: rkang g.yon lcags ris kyi g.yon du bskor ba'i do ra'i phyi dang /
NK014(pha)009:622: de ldog g.yas skor gyis nang du yangs pad skyur
NK014(pha)009:623: gtod dang rkang g.yas zur du phab nas rol 'gros
NK014(pha)009:625: chos kyi dbyings bskyed par bya ba'i phyir bskor ba lan gsum du bya ba /
NK014(pha)009:626: zhes lag gnyis phyir gdengs pa'i g.yas g.yon du g.yom 'gying /
NK014(pha)009:628: dzam chung nas rkang g.yas bteg ste g.yon gsigs kyi
NK014(pha)009:629: che lnga la bdun nas g.yas bskor du phyogs bzhir
NK014(pha)009:630: 'bebs shing / lnga pa mdun du 'gying bcas kyis
NK014(pha)009:631: 'bebs pa dang 'go brtsams pa'i mchongs pad yongs rdzogs
NK014(pha)009:633: bskyod 'gros mtshams chen nas rol 'gros la 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:635: snang srid rnams dbang du bsdu ba'i phyir g.yob mo lan gsum du bya ba /
NK014(pha)009:637: mchongs pad yongs rdzogs kyi pad skor rting mar phyag mtshan barje zhing rkang g.yas rgyab 'then /
NK014(pha)009:638: rnga gnyis brdeg theng ma chung gsum la lag gnyis
NK014(pha)009:639: pad chung gi dzam nas de bas chung gsum rol
NK014(pha)009:640: 'thab bcas par lag g.yon dkur brten te /
NK014(pha)009:641: sbir sbram zhes gsum la rkang g.yas 'degs 'jog gis /
NK014(pha)009:642: g.yon g.yas dbus rnams su 'gying gsig gi g.yob mo re byas te rol 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:644: mkha' 'gro rnams dpa' bskyed par bya ba'i phyir sig sig lan gsum du bya ba /
NK014(pha)009:646: bzhi pad yongs rdzogs kyi dang por phyag mtshan barje /
NK014(pha)009:649: rkang pa g.yas g.yon res brkyang gis g.yas dang /
NK014(pha)009:651: dbus rnams su gsig cing re re'i mtshams su sbram
NK014(pha)009:652: sbir sbram la g.yas g.yon du gcu ba'i len 'gying
NK014(pha)009:653: re byas nas mjug tu g.yas pa'i gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:654: mchongs pad song nas brtsams pa'i don gyis yangs pad gcig dang skyur gtod chig brdungs rol pa /
NK014(pha)009:657: dam nyams kyi bla 'gugs pa'i phyir mgo gug lan gsum du bya ba /
NK014(pha)009:659: bzhi pad song nas brtsam pa'i don gyi yangs pad gcig dang skyur gtod /
NK014(pha)009:661: lag dkur brten gyis rkang stabs dpa' bskyed ltar las
NK014(pha)009:662: g.yas g.yon dbus su gsig dus mgo gug tsam re
NK014(pha)009:668: dam can rnams 'bod par bya ba'i phyir spyugs pa lan gsum du 'don pa /
NK014(pha)009:672: lag gnyis kyi srin lag dang mathe'u chung gnyis mthe
NK014(pha)009:673: bong gis mnan cing gung mdzub brkyang ba kha'i thad
NK014(pha)009:674: du bsgyur zhing rnga che bzhir dbus su g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)009:675: re mos kyis gsig pa dang spyugs pa re bton
NK014(pha)009:681: steng byin gyis rlob par bya ba'i phyir gnam 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad du bri ba /
NK014(pha)009:683: bzhi pad yongs rdzogs kyi rting mar rkang g.yas rgyab 'then dang /
NK014(pha)009:684: pad chung gi dzam gsum nas /
NK014(pha)009:685: lag g.yon dkur brten cing rkang g.yas g.yon pa'i barla
NK014(pha)009:686: la gtad la g.yon 'phar gsigs kyis g.yas bskor du
NK014(pha)009:687: chig brdeg brgyad kyi bar phur rtses steng du rtsibs
NK014(pha)009:688: brgyad bri tshul gyis dal bus skor rjes /
NK014(pha)009:692: bskyed 'gros mtshams chung nas chig brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:694: bar byin gyis rlob par bya ba'i phyir logs bkra shis rtags brgyad du bri ba /
NK014(pha)009:697: gzhan sngar ltar las phur rtse logs bstan gyis bri tshul /
NK014(pha)009:699: 'og byin gyis rlob par bya ba'i phyir sa pad+ma 'dab brgyad du bri ba /
NK014(pha)009:700: sngar ltar las phur rtse 'og bstan gyis bri tshul /
NK014(pha)009:701: rjes su mtshams chen nas rol 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:703: rdo rje phyed 'gros kyis sa btsal ba /
NK014(pha)009:705: sbram sbram zhes pa'i len nas /
NK014(pha)009:707: bzhi grangs gnyis la mchongs pad song don gyi yangs
NK014(pha)009:708: pad skyur gtod dang rkang g.yon bteg pa'i len nas
NK014(pha)009:709: / bzhi grangs gsum gyi re re la /
NK014(pha)009:712: thugs ka bsnol ba dang bstun nas rim par rkang
NK014(pha)009:713: g.yon rgyab tu bskum pa'i g.yas pa 'gro phyogs kyi
NK014(pha)009:717: de'i ngang nas lag pad skyur dang bstun bzhi brdeg
NK014(pha)009:718: che ba gcig la rkang g.yas g.yas su mchongs stabs
NK014(pha)009:721: gcig ces rkang g.yas mdun du phab pa'i lcags mda'
NK014(pha)009:722: dang lag dkur brten gyi ngang nas gnyis gnyis zhes
NK014(pha)009:723: de khar 'gying yang rkang pa g.yon pas ldog ste
NK014(pha)009:724: sngar ltar rwa btsal nas g.yon du mchongs mthar lag
NK014(pha)009:725: dkur brten gyi rkang g.yon mdun du gcig ces phab
NK014(pha)009:726: nas / gnyis gnyis zhes bzhi brdungs ldem 'gros la 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:728: ldem 'gros kyi g.yon pa'i gsum thog nas /
NK014(pha)009:729: rdo rje brkyangs 'gros kyis sa 'dul ba /
NK014(pha)009:730: bzhi brdeg gnyis kyi dang por g.yas dang /
NK014(pha)009:731: gnyis pa'i gcig gnyis la g.yon du g.yom 'gying /
NK014(pha)009:732: gsum bzhi nas brtsams te grangs phyed len gyis rtsis
NK014(pha)009:733: pa'i bzhi grangs gnyis gnyis la yangs pad skyur gtod
NK014(pha)009:734: rnams rdzogs pa re byas pa'i bzhi pad yongs rdzogs
NK014(pha)009:735: kyi pad skor rting ma len dus rkang g.yas kyis
NK014(pha)009:736: lte ba bskor rjes 'gro phyogs su rkang g.yas kyi
NK014(pha)009:737: phyed 'gros ltar rwa btsal ba'i dbus rwa rdzogs pa
NK014(pha)009:738: dang / gcig la rkang g.yas phab /
NK014(pha)009:739: gnyis gnyis la b+han phur gdengs rkang g.yon bteg cing /
NK014(pha)009:740: g.yas pa'i rting gsig gis yongs phyogs su kha bsgyur
NK014(pha)009:741: nas rkang g.yon gyis rwa gsum btsal la g.yon du
NK014(pha)009:742: mchongs mthar sngar bzhin bzhi brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:744: ldem 'gros g.yon pa'i gsum thog nas /
NK014(pha)009:745: rdo rje sbag 'gros kyis sa gzhi byin gyis rlob pa /
NK014(pha)009:746: bzhi grangs phyed gnyis la g.yom 'gying /
NK014(pha)009:747: mchongs pad song brtsams kyis yangs pad nas len gyi bar phyed 'gros ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:748: rkang pa g.yas pa do ra'i nang du rwa gsum /
NK014(pha)009:750: gnyis gnyis la brkyang ma ltar bskor nas /
NK014(pha)009:751: g.yon pas yongs phyogs su rwa gsum /
NK014(pha)009:753: gnyis gnyis la g.yas bteg nas rgyab tu g.yas pas rwa gsum /
NK014(pha)009:754: sngar ltar bskor te g.yon pas 'gro phyogs su rwa gsum btsal nas /
NK014(pha)009:755: g.yon du mchongs mthar ldem 'gros la sngar bzhin bcug /
NK014(pha)009:756: de'i ngang nas g.yas pa'i gsum thog mchongs pad song
NK014(pha)009:757: nas brtsams zhes bzhi brdungs g.yom 'gying yangs pad skyur
NK014(pha)009:758: gtod / rol pa rnams byas la /
NK014(pha)009:759: bskyod 'gros mtshams chen nas rol 'gros la 'jug pa'o //
NK014(pha)009:762: brten pa bskyed pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)009:764: mkha' rlung rak+ta zhing chen dang //
NK014(pha)009:765: keng rus me dkyil gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)009:768: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK014(pha)009:770: rnga bzhi brdungs la bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:771: bzhi pad song don gyi yangs pad skyur gtod dang rkang g.yon bteg len nas /
NK014(pha)009:772: rkang pa lcags ris dang stod g.yon g.yas su gcu
NK014(pha)009:773: zhing lag phyed pad phyir g.yugs kyi rnam pa'i g.yom
NK014(pha)009:774: gsig gsum / gcig la rkang g.yas mdun drang por mchongs 'bebs dang /
NK014(pha)009:775: gnyis gnyis la g.yon bteg g.yas pa'i rting gsigs kyis
NK014(pha)009:776: rgyab zur nang logs tsam du phab nas g.yom gsig
NK014(pha)009:777: gsum / de bzhin du bar rnams la bzhi grangs
NK014(pha)009:778: chung ba rer g.yon pa'i mkhrig ma nas phur dar
NK014(pha)009:779: 'dren bzhin du dzam khrud kyis g.yas su bskor te
NK014(pha)009:780: gsum / / gcig ces par rkang g.yas do ra'i
NK014(pha)009:781: rgyab zur dang do ra'i rgyab tu kha blta ba'i
NK014(pha)009:783: gnyis gnyis la g.yon bteg nas snga ma snga ma'i
NK014(pha)009:784: rkang g.yas kyi shul du phab pas chos 'byung gi
NK014(pha)009:786: g.yom gsig gsum re'i rting ma rdzogs rjes dzam khrud kyis nang du kha bsgyur nas /
NK014(pha)009:788: mchongs pad song brtsams rol pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:789: bskyod 'gros mtshams chung nas chig brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:791: 'thor byed rlung nag tshogs kyis rgya gram gtams //
NK014(pha)009:793: sbram sbram gyi len nas lnga brdungs kyi /
NK014(pha)009:794: dang po che brdeg la bzhi pad song don gyi
NK014(pha)009:795: yangs pad skyur gtod bzhi phan la rdzogs nas lnga
NK014(pha)009:797: gnyis pa chung brdeg la b+han phur gyen bstan mdun mnyam gyi dzam len rjes /
NK014(pha)009:798: che chung spel ma bzhi la /
NK014(pha)009:799: rkang lag g.yas g.yon mthun par mdun phyogs su nang skor phyed pa re dang /
NK014(pha)009:800: phyi skor phyed pa re gzhu dbyibs ltar bskor nas che brdeg la mchongs pad song /
NK014(pha)009:801: lnga brdeg dal mnyam gcig gi gcig gnyis la phur dar phyir bskor gyis g.yas su gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:802: gsum dang bzhi la rkang pa g.yon g.yas 'degs 'jog dang /
NK014(pha)009:803: lnga la g.yon bteg 'bebs kyi len pa lnga brdungs rol pa nas /
NK014(pha)009:804: bskyod 'gros mtshams chung chig brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:806: chags pa rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba klong 'khyil //
NK014(pha)009:807: g.yom 'gying sngar ltar lnga brdungs kyi bzhi pad song /
NK014(pha)009:809: lnga brdeg che chung spel ma bzhi la /
NK014(pha)009:810: lan gcig shos dkur brten te g.yas g.yon mchan khung
NK014(pha)009:811: nas phyir bskor dang bstun rkang pa g.yas g.yon gyis
NK014(pha)009:812: phyir bskor zlum po re dang /
NK014(pha)009:813: lag gnyis sgeg mo'i tshul gyi rkang g.yas g.yas su phab pa la g.yon pas nang bskor gcig dang /
NK014(pha)009:814: mdun du yangs pad skyur gtod chung ba gcig la g.yas su mchongs pad song /
NK014(pha)009:816: bskyod chung nas chig brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:818: zhing chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi mtha' dbus brdal //
NK014(pha)009:820: sbram sbram gyi len nas rnga bzhi brdungs la bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:821: bzhi pad song don gyi yangs pad skyur gtod len nas /
NK014(pha)009:822: rkang lag rdo rje phyed 'gros ltar las dbus rwa dor te /
NK014(pha)009:823: rkang pa g.yas pas do ra'i nang zur gyi g.yon dang g.yas su gru re btsal nas /
NK014(pha)009:824: gcig ces par g.yas gsigs dang /
NK014(pha)009:825: gnyis gnyis la g.yas 'degs 'jog gis g.yon bskor du
NK014(pha)009:826: phyir log ste rkang g.yon pas do ra'i rgyab zur
NK014(pha)009:827: g.yas g.yon du gru re btsal rjes /
NK014(pha)009:828: phyed 'gros ltar g.yon mchongs len nas bzhi brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:830: keng rus brtsegs pa'i ri rab me chen 'bar //
NK014(pha)009:832: mchongs pad song don gyi yangs pad skyur gtod nas /
NK014(pha)009:834: lag gnyis gyen bstan gyis cung 'gying rjes /
NK014(pha)009:835: rkang g.yas zol bteg gis nang bskor dang lag gnyis
NK014(pha)009:836: g.yas phyogs nas gar bskor gyis bzhi grangs gcig la
NK014(pha)009:837: 'gying nas / gcig gnyis la rkang lag mnyam du 'gro phyogs su 'bebs cing gseg /
NK014(pha)009:838: yang gsum bzhi la lag gyen bstan dang /
NK014(pha)009:839: bzhi grangs phyed gnyis la rkang lag ldog pas phyir
NK014(pha)009:840: bskor nas yongs phyogs su 'bebs gsig g.yas pas sngar
NK014(pha)009:841: ltar nang bskor gyis 'gro phyogs su 'abebaba pa dang
NK014(pha)009:842: rkang g.yon spos nas bzhi 'gros gcig blangs te /
NK014(pha)009:843: kha nang du blta bas gcig gnyis zhes lan gnyis
NK014(pha)009:844: kyi bar lag gnyis thal sbyar gyis dbus su gsigs
NK014(pha)009:845: la / bzhi tshan gcig gis gcig gnyis la phyag rgya de g.yas su cung gzhol rjes /
NK014(pha)009:846: gsum bzhi nas mchongs pad song /
NK014(pha)009:848: bskyod chung nas gnyis gnyis zhes bzhi brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:850: ye shes 'bar ba'i me 'od kun tu 'phro //
NK014(pha)009:853: bzhi brdungs chung gnyis kyi dang por lag phur bu
NK014(pha)009:854: 'og nas b+han+d+hara gtod cing rkang g.yas 'gro phyogs su
NK014(pha)009:855: blta ba'i mdun nas g.yas zur gom do nur /
NK014(pha)009:856: gnyis par lag ldog ste rkang g.yon gyis g.yon zur du gom do nur rjes /
NK014(pha)009:857: bzhi brdungs che ba gcig la g.yas mchong gi rol len dang /
NK014(pha)009:859: gnyis gnyis la g.yas mdun phab kyis ldem 'gying rnams phyed 'gros ltar bya /
NK014(pha)009:860: yang g.yon nas brtsams te ldog pas gru gsum sngar ltar logs 'gro phyogs su bstan pa btsal nas /
NK014(pha)009:861: gcig ces par g.yon mdun du phab la bzhi brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:863: b+h+r+aum las dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)009:865: nyis brdungs 'thengs mar bsgyur ba'i mchongs pad song don gyi /
NK014(pha)009:866: nyis brdungs re la yangs pad skyur gtod re re dang /
NK014(pha)009:867: rol pa gsum nas lag res 'phyar dang rkang pa shud 'gros kyis /
NK014(pha)009:868: sgo khyud 'gram logs ya phubs sogs btsal ba'i sgo'i
NK014(pha)009:869: 'khyog mtshams rnams su rnga skad che ba re dang
NK014(pha)009:870: bstun lag gdengs tsam re byas nas 'khor mtshams /
NK014(pha)009:873: bskyod 'gros mtshams chen nas rol 'gros la 'jug pa'o //
NK014(pha)009:874: gnyis pa brten pa bskyed pa la /
NK014(pha)009:876: gtso bo dang ni rigs bzhi dang //
NK014(pha)009:877: rigs lnga'i yum dang goo r+ai brgyad //
NK014(pha)009:878: sid+ha ma brgyad sgo ma bzhi //
NK014(pha)009:879: dbang phyug ma dang phra men gyi //
NK014(pha)009:880: bam chen dpal chen stob 'chams so //
NK014(pha)009:882: dang po gtso bo dpal chen po'i 'gying 'chams kyi sdom ni /
NK014(pha)009:884: zhabs dang gdags rgyan byug rtsi dang //
NK014(pha)009:885: bgo ba'i gos dang khyung gshog go //
NK014(pha)009:888: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag rgya las dpal chen po'i 'gying chen /
NK014(pha)009:893: g.yas brkyang gis g.yas dang g.yon brkyang gis g.yon du gsig cing re re'i mjug tu 'grol bsdu /
NK014(pha)009:896: yang dbus su res brkyang gis che bzhir gsigs nas /
NK014(pha)009:900: bskyod 'gros mtshams chung nas chig brdungs ldem 'gros /
NK014(pha)009:906: lag gnyis dkur brten te che bzhir res brkyang gis dbus ma ltar gsigs rjes /
NK014(pha)009:913: dbu gsum rdzogs su bskyed pa /
NK014(pha)009:916: dzam chung dang bstun g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal /
NK014(pha)009:917: che bzhir g.yas g.yon dbus su gsig cing mtshams kyi
NK014(pha)009:918: 'grol bsdu pad dzam dang bcas pa 'gying chen ltar
NK014(pha)009:919: las / lag stabs kyi khyad par thal mo khong
NK014(pha)009:920: stong gi stangs ka g.yas g.yon dbus gsum gyi gsig
NK014(pha)009:921: las / dang bstun nas / rna ba g.yas dang /
NK014(pha)009:923: gdong thad rnams su gcu tsam re bya zhing /
NK014(pha)009:930: de'i ngang nas rkang g.yon 'degs gsig dang bstun /
NK014(pha)009:931: phyag drug rdzogs su bskyed pa las /
NK014(pha)009:932: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:933: dril bu dung dmar 'jig rten g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:937: che bzhir lag gnyis thugs kar bsnol nas rkang pa res brkyang gis dbus su gsig /
NK014(pha)009:941: che brdeg bzhi rer lag g.yon dkur brten dang g.yas rdo rje gdengs stabs kyi rgya mtho ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:942: ti ra'i rgya thad kar brgyangs nas rkang g.yas bteg
NK014(pha)009:943: 'bebs kyis g.yas phyogs su gsig 'gros re re dang
NK014(pha)009:944: / gnyis ka'i mjug tu g.yas gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:947: de bzhin du g.yas dkur brten dang g.yon dung dmar 'dzin rgya mtho ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:948: 'jig rten 'degs rgya thad kar brgyangs nas g.yon du gsig 'gros re re dang /
NK014(pha)009:949: gnyis ka'i mjug tu g.yon gzhol rjes snga mar pad dzam /
NK014(pha)009:954: zhabs bzhi rdzogs su bskyed pa /
NK014(pha)009:958: che bzhir lag gnyis pus steng du brkyang la rkang
NK014(pha)009:959: g.yas brkyang gis rnam pas g.yas g.yon du gcu zhing
NK014(pha)009:965: gdags pa'i rgyan gnyis kyi thog mar thod pa skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan /
NK014(pha)009:969: che lnga la b+han phur sbyar ba dpral ba'i dbus dang /
NK014(pha)009:971: rna ltag g.yas g.yon rnams su 'dzin rgya dang bstun gsigs la 'grol bsdu /
NK014(pha)009:975: 'dzag pa'i mgo bo lnga bcu'i do shal /
NK014(pha)009:977: bzhi pad song don gyi pad skyur gtod rjes /
NK014(pha)009:978: chung gsum la g.yas pas skra nas bzung ba'i b+han+d+ha
NK014(pha)009:979: rna ba g.yon pa'i thad du 'phyar ba che drug
NK014(pha)009:980: la de nyid nas dal bus bsus pa'i mtha' bskor
NK014(pha)009:981: te chung gsum la g.yas su 'phyar nas /
NK014(pha)009:982: che drug la sngar shul du ldog pa'i rjes kyi
NK014(pha)009:983: sbram drug ces par rkang g.yon bteg len gyis g.yas
NK014(pha)009:988: byug pa'i rtsi gsum gi thog mar rak+ta'i thig le /
NK014(pha)009:991: dzam chung ngus g.yas pa'i sor mo dbus ma gsum gyis b+han+d+ha nas rak+ta blangs te /
NK014(pha)009:992: che bzhir g.yas g.yon res gsig dang bstun gung mos smin phrag /
NK014(pha)009:993: srin mdzub kyis mkhur tshos gnyis /
NK014(pha)009:994: gung mos sna rtse dang ol ko rnams su thig
NK014(pha)009:995: le byas rjes phur rtse nang bskor phyir bstan gyis
NK014(pha)009:999: dzam chung ngus sngar bzhin thal chen blangs te /
NK014(pha)009:1000: che bzhir skra mtshams kyi dbus dang /
NK014(pha)009:1003: dpral ba rnams su tshom bu re byas la /
NK014(pha)009:1007: dzam chung ngus zhag blangs te /
NK014(pha)009:1008: lus mi gcu bar g.yon brkyang gis 'dug la /
NK014(pha)009:1009: sor mo bzhi brkyang bas che bzhir nu ma g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1010: nas g.yas kyi bar zlum mo phyed pa'i rnam par
NK014(pha)009:1016: bgo ba'i gos gsum gyi thog mar glang chen gyi ko rlon /
NK014(pha)009:1019: dzam chung la phur dar brgyangs te pags pa 'dzin tshul gyi /
NK014(pha)009:1020: che brdeg bzhi bzhir g.yas g.yon dbus gsum du gsig cing gzhol sogs mkha' 'gro dpa' bskyed bzhin las /
NK014(pha)009:1021: mjug tu bskyod chung chig ldem nas /
NK014(pha)009:1024: bzhi pad song don pad skyur gtod rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1026: phur dar brgyangs te bzung nas g.yas su 'phyar /
NK014(pha)009:1027: sbram la g.yon bteg len gyis gyon tshul byas te /
NK014(pha)009:1028: che bzhir kha phyir bltas kyis g.yas su 'phar gsig gis 'gro /
NK014(pha)009:1029: chung gsum la g.yas 'phyar gyi dzam len nas che
NK014(pha)009:1030: bzhir kha nang blta'i g.yas su 'phar gsig gis 'gro
NK014(pha)009:1031: / chung gsum la g.yas 'phyar 'gying dzam len nas che bzhir dbus su res gsig byas la /
NK014(pha)009:1039: dzam chung la phur dar bzung barla steng du brkyangs nas /
NK014(pha)009:1040: che bzhir g.yas g.yon res brkyang gi gsigs rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1043: chig rol bskyod chung nas chig ldem /
NK014(pha)009:1045: khams gsum zil gyis gnon pa rdo rje'i khyung gshog /
NK014(pha)009:1048: dzam chung nas g.yas g.yon dbus gsum du gsig pa 'gying chen ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1049: snga ma gnyis la g.yas g.yon gyi gzhol te mos kyi rjes su yangs pad dzam chung /
NK014(pha)009:1050: dbus gsig gi rjes su g.yas gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:1053: bskyod 'gros mtshams chen nas rol 'gros la 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:1054: gnyis pa rigs bzhi'i gyad 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1055: chig brdeg rol 'gros kyi ngang nas rigs bzhi khro bo'i gyad 'chams las /
NK014(pha)009:1056: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i phyag rgya /
NK014(pha)009:1060: g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus smug zhal //
NK014(pha)009:1061: che bzhir b+han phur rna ba'i g.yas g.yon du /
NK014(pha)009:1062: thal mo phyir bstan pa bzung ste dbu gsum gyi tshul gyis gtso bo'i 'gying chung ltar gsigs nas /
NK014(pha)009:1064: yangs pad kyi phur dar skyur ba nas dzam chung rdzogs pa'i bar der /
NK014(pha)009:1065: 'khor lo rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:1066: dril bu dung dmar tri shul g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:1067: che ba bzhi tshan gsum gyi /
NK014(pha)009:1068: dang por lag gnyis thugs kar bsnol //
NK014(pha)009:1069: gnyis par lag gnyis mtho bar brgyangs //
NK014(pha)009:1070: gsum par thad kar brgyangs te sngar bzhin gsigs la
NK014(pha)009:1071: re re'i mjug tu 'grol bsdu pad dzam re byas
NK014(pha)009:1072: pa'i rting ma dzam chung gi dus /
NK014(pha)009:1073: zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum stabs //
NK014(pha)009:1074: che bzhir lag gnyis dkur brten nas gsigs rjes //
NK014(pha)009:1078: bskyod chung nas chig ldem mo //
NK014(pha)009:1079: rigs gzhan gsum yang phyag rgya bsgyur kha tsam ma gtogs de dang 'dra zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1080: karma he ru ka rdzogs rjes bskyod 'gros mtshams chen nas rol 'gros la 'jug pa khyad par ro //
NK014(pha)009:1082: rigs snga ma gsum po'i zhabs song rjes kyi yangs
NK014(pha)009:1083: pad dang bstun rang gi phyi ma'i rigs de'i 'chams
NK014(pha)009:1085: deng sang phyag len la'ang 'di mdzad do //
NK014(pha)009:1086: de la so so'i phyag rgya ni /
NK014(pha)009:1087: rat+na he ru ka'i phyag rgya /
NK014(pha)009:1088: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK014(pha)009:1089: riin chen rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:1090: dril bu dung dmar dgra s+t+wa g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:1091: zhabs bzhi pad+ma he ru ka'i phyag rgya /
NK014(pha)009:1092: g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus dmar zhal //
NK014(pha)009:1093: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:1094: dril bu dung dmar rnge'u chung g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:1095: zhabs bzhi karma he ru ka'i phyag rgya /
NK014(pha)009:1096: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK014(pha)009:1097: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)009:1098: dril bu dung dmar thong gshol g.yon //
NK014(pha)009:1099: zhabs bzhi gsum pa rigs lnga'i yum gyi 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1101: rigs lnga yum gyi phyag rgya /
NK014(pha)009:1105: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rigs kyi mdog /
NK014(pha)009:1106: che bzhir b+han phur zhal thad du gtso bo'i dbus zhal ltar gsig nas /
NK014(pha)009:1110: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la brten //
NK014(pha)009:1111: lag g.yon dkur brten dang bcas yab kyi mgul nas
NK014(pha)009:1112: 'khyud rgyas rkang pa g.yas brkyang gis che bzhir g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1115: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK014(pha)009:1116: lag g.yas dkur brten cing g.yon du dung dmar stob
NK014(pha)009:1117: tshul gyis che bzhir rkang g.yon bteg 'gying nas 'grol
NK014(pha)009:1119: kro d+h+ai rigs lnga dbyings kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)009:1120: che bzhir lag 'khyud rgya dang rkang g.yas bteg 'gying nas /
NK014(pha)009:1125: bzhi pa goo r+ai brgyad kyi 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1126: khro mo brgyad kyi brjid 'chams las /
NK014(pha)009:1127: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK014(pha)009:1128: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK014(pha)009:1130: lnga brdungs che chung spel mar bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1131: che brdeg la bzhi pad song don gyi yangs pad skyur gtod dang /
NK014(pha)009:1132: chung brdeg la b+han phur mdun mnyam gyi dzam yan rlung dkyil dang 'dra /
NK014(pha)009:1133: de nas lag g.yas phur pa 'phyar stabs dang g.yon b+han+d+ha thugs kar gyen bstan gyis bzung nas /
NK014(pha)009:1134: rkang gnyis lcags mda' g.yon brkyang gi che brdeg la g.yas zur du 'then gsig dang /
NK014(pha)009:1135: chung brdeg la yangs pad re /
NK014(pha)009:1136: de ltar spel ba thengs gsum gyi mthar /
NK014(pha)009:1138: che brdeg la mdun du yangs pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1139: chung brdeg gi gcig gnyis la g.yas su yangs pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1140: gsum nas rkang g.yas g.yon bskor gyi kha phyir bltas
NK014(pha)009:1141: te mda' gzhu 'gengs rgyas g.yas su 'then gsig dang
NK014(pha)009:1142: / yangs pad spel ba thengs gsum gyi mthar /
NK014(pha)009:1143: 'grol bsdus kha nang du bsgyur rjes mdun du yangs pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1146: bskyod 'gros mtshams chung nas chig ldem mo //
NK014(pha)009:1147: pra mo sogs drug kyang phyag rgya'i bsgyur kha ma gtogs 'dra ba las /
NK014(pha)009:1148: tsan+da'i rjes su bskyod chen nas rol 'gros so //
NK014(pha)009:1149: so so'i phyag rgya'i khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)009:1150: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK014(pha)009:1151: bee ta byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK014(pha)009:1152: zhes pa'i snga ma nang du lag g.yon b+han+d+ha kha
NK014(pha)009:1153: sbub pa'i steng du g.yas pa'i lag ngar sgreng ba
NK014(pha)009:1155: phyi ma rgyab tu lag g.yas 'phyar stabs dang g.yon b+han+d+ha sbub pa kha'i thad du 'dzin pa'o //
NK014(pha)009:1158: snga ma nang du b+han+d+ha barla g.yon thad bzung ba'i
NK014(pha)009:1159: skra nyag lag g.yas pas nu g.yas kyi thad du
NK014(pha)009:1160: brkyang nas 'dzin pa rgyu ma 'dren tshul dang /
NK014(pha)009:1161: phyi ma rgyab tu b+han+d+ha thugs kar bzung ba phur
NK014(pha)009:1162: rtses lan gsum dkrugs nas zhal du gsol tshul dang
NK014(pha)009:1164: sme sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK014(pha)009:1166: snga ma nang du b+han phur zhal gyi thad du
NK014(pha)009:1167: mnyam par bzung rjes lag gnyis bshad kyis bskyod pa
NK014(pha)009:1168: dang / phyi ma rgyab tu b+han phur barla g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1169: pa'i thad du bzung ba'i skra nas g.yas pas bzung
NK014(pha)009:1170: ba gtod pa dang mnyam du phur dar phrag g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1171: dang / par 'gel ba'o // lnga pa sed+ha ma brgyad kyi 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1172: phra men brgyad kyi shon 'chams las /
NK014(pha)009:1173: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK014(pha)009:1174: b+y+aa g+h+ri gnas ltag bsnol mar stag /
NK014(pha)009:1176: bzhi brdung 'theng ma che chung spel mar bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1177: bzhi pad song nas brtsams pa'i bzhi brdungs che skad kyi /
NK014(pha)009:1178: gcig la pad skor gnyis la skyur /
NK014(pha)009:1181: chung brdeg la mdun mnyam gyi dzam len nas lag
NK014(pha)009:1182: gnyis dpung par bsnol ba'i rgyas rkang g.yas mdun du
NK014(pha)009:1183: btad nas che brdeg pa g.yas gsig gnyis dang /
NK014(pha)009:1184: chung brdeg la rkang g.yas g.yas zur du 'then 'gying gi len te /
NK014(pha)009:1185: de ltar spel ba thengs gsum dang lag gnyis lte
NK014(pha)009:1186: bar sor mo mthur bstan gyis bsnol ba'i rgyas che
NK014(pha)009:1187: brdeg la sngar bzhin g.yas gsig gnyis dang /
NK014(pha)009:1188: chung brdeg la len 'gying spel ba thengs gsum nas /
NK014(pha)009:1191: bzhi brdeg 'theng med dal ba gcig gi /
NK014(pha)009:1193: gnyis dang gsum la rkang g.yon g.yas bteg 'bebs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1194: bzhi la g.yon 'degs 'jog gi len nas /
NK014(pha)009:1196: sri la sogs drug la'ang 'chams tshul de dang 'dra ba las so so'i phyag rgya bsgyur zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1197: u l+au'i rjes su bskyod chen nas rol 'gros so //
NK014(pha)009:1198: so so'i phyag rgya'i khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)009:1199: sri gal nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK014(pha)009:1200: shwa na 'dral lta mthing kha spyang //
NK014(pha)009:1201: zhes pa'i snga mar b+han phur mnyam pa zhal thad g.yas g.yon du 'dzin pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1202: phyi ma lag gnyis thugs kar phyir bstan mnyam pa la lta zhing g.yas g.yon du brgyang ba'o //
NK014(pha)009:1203: gri d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK014(pha)009:1204: kang+ka kang phrag snar mgo ring /
NK014(pha)009:1205: snga ma barla g.yon thad gzung ba'i b+han skra'i nyag ma g.yas nu g.yas thad du 'dren tshul dang /
NK014(pha)009:1206: phyi ma phur dar dang b+han skra gnyis phrag g.yas g.yon du so sor bkal ba'o //
NK014(pha)009:1207: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK014(pha)009:1208: u lu lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK014(pha)009:1209: snga ma lag g.yon thugs kar b+han+d+ha gyen bstan dang
NK014(pha)009:1210: g.yas srin lag dang mathe'u chung gnyis mthe bong gi
NK014(pha)009:1211: bsnan nas gung mdzub sgreng ba gri rgya 'debs tshul
NK014(pha)009:1212: dang / phyi ma lag g.yon sngar ltar dang g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1213: khu tshur las mdzub mo lcags kyu ltar byas pas
NK014(pha)009:1214: dang / 'dren tshul lo // drug pa sgo ma bzhi'i 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1215: sgo skyong gdong mo bzhi'i rngams 'chams las /
NK014(pha)009:1216: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK014(pha)009:1217: kha do ra'i phyir bltas te //
NK014(pha)009:1220: bzhi pad song don gyi yangs pad nas len gyi rdo rje phyed 'gros ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1221: bzhi grangs gsum la mkha' dkyil ltar g.yon gsig gsum byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1223: gnyis gnyis zhes par lag g.yas u lu lta bu'i
NK014(pha)009:1224: rgyas lcags kyu 'degs tshul gyis rkang bteg pa'i g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1226: bzhi brdeg gcig gi gcig gnyis la rkang g.yas 'bebs
NK014(pha)009:1227: shing g.yon rgyab tu bskum pa dang lag gnyis thugs
NK014(pha)009:1229: gsum bzhi la lag pad bskor gyi rgya dkrol zhing rkang g.yas g.yas su bskor ba'i len nas /
NK014(pha)009:1231: dang po gcig gnyis la g.yas der phab cing g.yon grud tsam bya /
NK014(pha)009:1232: gsum bzhi la sngar ltar lag pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1233: rkang g.yas g.yon bskor gyi len nas gnyis pa'i gcig gnyis la /
NK014(pha)009:1234: rkang g.yon g.yon du 'degs 'bebs grud bcas dang /
NK014(pha)009:1235: gsum bzhi la rkang g.yon g.yas ldog pa'i len bya /
NK014(pha)009:1236: gsum pa'i gcig gnyis la rkang g.yas g.yas su 'degs 'bebs nas gsum bzhi la ldog pa'i bar der /
NK014(pha)009:1237: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK014(pha)009:1238: zhes brda' sbyar nas g.yom gsig gsum sogs 'chams tshul gzhan sngar ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1239: phyag rgya ni gcig gcig la lag g.yon pa'i steng
NK014(pha)009:1240: du g.yas sdigs mdzub mthur bstan gyis phyir bskor ba
NK014(pha)009:1241: / gnyis gnyis la de nyid gyen bstan gyi g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1242: pa'i nang nas phyir skyur ba zhags rgyas 'ching tshul
NK014(pha)009:1243: / dang / de bzhin du 'chams skad gtod tshul sogs sngar ji lta ba las /
NK014(pha)009:1244: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK014(pha)009:1245: zhes pa lag gnyis khu tshur gyen bstan las mdzub
NK014(pha)009:1246: mo dang mathe'u chung brkyang ba lcags sgrog gi rgya
NK014(pha)009:1247: dang / spyang gdong ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK014(pha)009:1248: zhes pa lag g.yas dpung pa'i nang thad du mkhrig
NK014(pha)009:1249: ma nang du bkug nas dril bu 'khrol tshul te
NK014(pha)009:1250: / dril bu ma'i bzhi grangs gsum po rdzogs rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1251: 'grol bsdus do ra'i nang du kha bsgyur nas /
NK014(pha)009:1252: bzhi brdungs kyi mchongs pad song don gyis yangs pad /
NK014(pha)009:1256: dbang phyug ma las bzhi'i 'dur 'chams mchongs pad song nas brtsams /
NK014(pha)009:1258: nyes brdungs 'theng ma'i yangs pad skyur gtod /
NK014(pha)009:1260: lag g.yas 'phyar zhing g.yon dkur brten te shud 'gros kyis cung zad phyin nas rkang g.yon thog /
NK014(pha)009:1261: shar nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK014(pha)009:1262: khyod kyis zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)009:1263: ces pa nas shugs cher btang ste /
NK014(pha)009:1264: bro ra zlum por bskor nas 'gro ba ni shar gyi ma bdun gyi 'dur 'chams so //
NK014(pha)009:1265: de nyid las mchongs pad song /
NK014(pha)009:1267: lag stabs ldog ste gru bzhir bskor ba lho'i ma bdun te /
NK014(pha)009:1268: lho nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK014(pha)009:1269: khyod kyis rgyas pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)009:1270: de bzhin du mtshams su mchongs pad song brtsams dang rol pa nas lag ldog ste /
NK014(pha)009:1272: gru gsum du bskor bas 'gro ba nub dang byang gi ma bdun te /
NK014(pha)009:1273: nub nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK014(pha)009:1274: khyod kyis dbang gi las mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)009:1275: byang nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK014(pha)009:1276: khyod kyis drag po'i las mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)009:1279: brgyad pa phra men ma'i bam len gyi 'chams /
NK014(pha)009:1282: spros te stob pa dang gsum /
NK014(pha)009:1285: sbrul nag 'khyil 'gros kyis btsal ba gnyis las /
NK014(pha)009:1288: bam rol bas btsal ba mchongs pad song nas brtsams zhes g.yon len yangs pad skyur gtod dang /
NK014(pha)009:1289: rol pa gsum nas lag gnyis g.yon g.yas su khyer
NK014(pha)009:1290: ba'i rol pa dang rkang pa shud 'gros drag cing
NK014(pha)009:1291: myur la khro bo'i gdangs mig gis kun tu blta
NK014(pha)009:1293: bam sbrul nag 'khyil 'gros kyis btsal ba mchongs pad song nas brtsams zhes pad rol sngar ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1294: lag g.yon dkur brten dang g.yas steng du 'phyar nas
NK014(pha)009:1295: seng ge ltar 'gying bzhin du shud 'gros kyis 'gro
NK014(pha)009:1296: bas ji ltar rigs pa bskor rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1297: lag gnyis gdengs te bya rgod lding ba ltar 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)009:1298: sbrul 'khor ba bzhin du 'khyil bskor bya zhing 'gugs
NK014(pha)009:1299: mtshams su rnga drag tu brdungs shing lag gnyis rol
NK014(pha)009:1300: pa dang lus bcums te dur bya 'dur ba ltar
NK014(pha)009:1302: 'chams dpon gyis b+han+d+ha'i skra nas bzung ba brnar te rol dpon gyi mdun du slebs pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1303: rkang g.yon thog kha sbub tu bzhag nas zem 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1304: la 'jug pa dang mnyam du 'chams pa gzhan rnams
NK014(pha)009:1305: b+han+d+ha brnar te shud 'gros rang gis 'gro zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1306: 'chams dpon rang gi b+han+d+ha'i thad du 'khor mtshams thams
NK014(pha)009:1307: cad kyis b+han+d+ha kha sbub tu bzhag nas 'chams dpon
NK014(pha)009:1311: rdor 'gros kyis brtag pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)009:1313: zem gyi ngang nas rang rang gi b+han+d+ha'i thad du slebs pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1314: bam rde'usa brtag pa dang po mchongs pad song nas brtsam /
NK014(pha)009:1316: nyis brdungs 'thengs ma gsum la lag g.yon dkur brten
NK014(pha)009:1317: dang g.yas g.yob cing g.yas kyi rgyab zur du gom
NK014(pha)009:1318: gsum nur nas / bzhi brdungs drag pa gcig la
NK014(pha)009:1319: g.yas sdigs mdzub b+han+d+ha la stob cing rkang g.yas brkyang
NK014(pha)009:1320: nas h+au lu'i sdang mig gis nang du gsig 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1321: gsum nur nas / gsum dang / yangs pad rol
NK014(pha)009:1322: pa nas g.yon gyi rgyab zur dang nang du tshul
NK014(pha)009:1323: de nyid rkang lag ldog pas byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1325: lag gnyis mtheb mdzub sprad pa'i rde'u 'bebs tshul dang
NK014(pha)009:1326: mig zur b+han+d+ha la blta bas rkang g.yon sngon 'gro'i
NK014(pha)009:1328: phur dar 'khrig ma nas 'dren bzhin du bred tshul
NK014(pha)009:1329: gyis g.yon brkyang ba'i zur 'then bzhis phyir rgyang gi
NK014(pha)009:1330: 'ong ba bya rog gra 'thengs kyi 'gros de nyid
NK014(pha)009:1332: nang gi 'thengs nas bzhi bzhi zhes rkang g.yas phyir
NK014(pha)009:1333: bskor bas blangs pa'i zem 'gros kyis tab tab por
NK014(pha)009:1334: bskor lam la zhugs te 'khor mtshams /
NK014(pha)009:1335: bam rde'usa brtag pa gnyis pa mchongs pad song nas brtsam /
NK014(pha)009:1336: zhes sngar ji lta ba bzhin ldab /
NK014(pha)009:1337: slar yang zem gyis so so'i b+han+d+ha la bskor ba 'khor mtshams /
NK014(pha)009:1338: bam barde'usa brtag pa gsum pa mchongs pad song nas brtsam /
NK014(pha)009:1339: zhes sngar ltar ldabs nas zem gyis bskor lam 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:1340: lan rjes ma gnyis snga ma las cung zad snying
NK014(pha)009:1341: khams je cher song tshul gyis nang du bam la
NK014(pha)009:1342: nye bar 'gro zhing phyir 'gros chung du gtong ba
NK014(pha)009:1343: khyad par ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:1345: bam rdo rje 'gros kyis brtag pa mchongs pad song nas brtsam /
NK014(pha)009:1347: phod sham thu bar bsdus nas tsog pur 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)009:1348: mkha' dkyil lta bu'i bzhi brdungs kyis stod g.yom gsum nas /
NK014(pha)009:1349: che bzhir g.yas su rdor 'gros gsum dang /
NK014(pha)009:1350: yang g.yom gsum nas g.yon mdun bstan gyi nang du
NK014(pha)009:1351: rdor 'gros gsum phyin nas bzhi brdeg gnyis kyi dang
NK014(pha)009:1352: po'i gcig gnyis la bred bzhin du b+han+d+ha'i skra nas
NK014(pha)009:1353: 'then te grud pa shwa na'i brtul zhugs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1354: gsum bzhi la dri snom pa sri la'i brtul zhugs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1355: gnyis pa'i gcig gnyis la bam 'gre ldog sgyur ba
NK014(pha)009:1356: mtshon byed b+han+d+ha kha gyen du bsgyur ba stag gi
NK014(pha)009:1357: brtul zhugs te snying khams rim gyis bskyed nas gsum
NK014(pha)009:1358: bzhi la langs te zem la 'jug go //
NK014(pha)009:1359: skabs 'dir rdor 'gros kyis brtag pa lan gsum ldabs nas dang por skra nas 'then /
NK014(pha)009:1361: gsum par 'gre ldog byed pa sogs yig rnying dag
NK014(pha)009:1362: las 'byung zhing bya gcan so so'i rnam 'gyur dang
NK014(pha)009:1363: sbyar te phra men so so'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK014(pha)009:1364: 'jug tshul dang / khro bo'i gyad stobs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1365: dpa' bo'i 'jug 'gros la sogs pa'i 'gros dang /
NK014(pha)009:1367: gdangs skad kyi bsgyur tshul sogs rgyud dang man ngag
NK014(pha)009:1368: rnams las rgya cher gsungs pa mthong yang ha cang
NK014(pha)009:1369: mang bas 'jigs phyir re zhig de tsam ste /
NK014(pha)009:1370: spro na ji ltar rigs pa sbyar bas chog cing /
NK014(pha)009:1371: rde'u'i 'go'i g.yab mo la'ang deng sang nang 'jug kyang
NK014(pha)009:1372: phyir 'gro ltar 'thengs skad kyi gom nur byed na'ang
NK014(pha)009:1373: mkhas pa 'dar sogs kyi yig rnying las 'dir bkod
NK014(pha)009:1375: gang ltar kyang 'di dag bla na med pa'i rgyud
NK014(pha)009:1376: kyi gsang ba'i spyod pa rmad du byung ba yin
NK014(pha)009:1377: pas bro mkhan gyi brtul zhugs kho na lta bur
NK014(pha)009:1378: len pa rnams dang ma 'dres par byed pa gces
NK014(pha)009:1382: zhes spyugs pa'i sgras 'bod cing rol 'bebs dang bstun /
NK014(pha)009:1383: sngar ltar tsog pur 'dug ste g.yom gsum nas rdor
NK014(pha)009:1384: 'gros kyis b+han+d+ha'i rtsar phyin la rus sbal gyi stabs
NK014(pha)009:1385: sam phyed skyil gang rung gis 'dug la /
NK014(pha)009:1386: lnga brdungs che chung spel mar bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1387: bzhi pad yongs rdzogs dang chung skad la g.yas su len pad gcig nas /
NK014(pha)009:1388: 'di man thams cad du chung res la yangs pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1389: che res la so so'i phyag rgya bsgyur ba gnyis spel ma kho na ste /
NK014(pha)009:1390: so so'i phyag rgya la gsum /
NK014(pha)009:1395: che brdeg re la lag g.yas 'phyar gyis g.yas phyogs nas g.yobs pas zhi ba'i lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK014(pha)009:1396: de bzhin du g.yon g.yob kyis khro bo'i lha tshogs /
NK014(pha)009:1397: mdun mnyam g.yob kyis bla ma /
NK014(pha)009:1398: g.yas kyi rgyab zur nas g.yas pas g.yob pas dam can pho rgyud /
NK014(pha)009:1399: de ldog g.yob pas mo rgyud rnams spyan drang ba'o //
NK014(pha)009:1400: gnyis pa yang che brdeg re la g.yon pa'i khu
NK014(pha)009:1401: tshur gyi steng g.yas skyabs sbyin me long gi rgyas
NK014(pha)009:1402: gzugs / g.yon khu tshur sgreng ba'i mkhrig mar g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1403: pa'i gung mdzub kyis bskul ba pi wang gi rgyas
NK014(pha)009:1404: gzugs / sgra / lag gnyis thal mo phyir bstan gyi rgyas dri mchog /
NK014(pha)009:1405: de nyid gyen bstan gyi rgyas ro mchog /
NK014(pha)009:1406: lag gnyis kyi phur dar brkyang nas 'phyar ba'i rgyas reg bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:1407: bam bsgral bya kun 'dus kyi rnam par gsal ba
NK014(pha)009:1408: nyid ngo bo 'dod yon lngar byin gyis rlob pa'o
NK014(pha)009:1413: dpral ba'i thad rnams su phur bsgril re dang /
NK014(pha)009:1414: g.yas su bdar nas bam la btab ste bsgral de rjes g.yas pas phur bu btab nas g.yon dang /
NK014(pha)009:1415: lhan cig pas rim pa bzhin stob pa bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:1419: dbus su bla ma rnams smin mtshams kyi thad tsam nas 'bul lo //
NK014(pha)009:1420: g.yas kyi rgyab zur du dam can pho rgyud dang /
NK014(pha)009:1421: g.yon gyi rgyab zur du dam can mo rgyud gnyis la dpung pa'i thad tsam nas 'bul /
NK014(pha)009:1422: g.yas su grogs pho rgyud dang /
NK014(pha)009:1423: g.yon du grogs mo rgyud rnams la rang gi rkang pa'i thad tsam nas stob /
NK014(pha)009:1424: de nas rang nyid longs spyod tshul /
NK014(pha)009:1425: am phrag tu 'jug tshul rnams byas rjes rol mo chem brdungs la /
NK014(pha)009:1426: lag g.yon b+han+d+ha'i skra nas bzung /
NK014(pha)009:1427: g.yas phur pa sa la btsugs nas mi theg cing
NK014(pha)009:1428: 'dar ba'i tshul cung zad byas la dal bus langs
NK014(pha)009:1429: te / rkang g.yon len 'degs dang mnyam du b+han+d+ha
NK014(pha)009:1430: phrag la bkal te nyis brdungs 'thengs ma drag la
NK014(pha)009:1431: myur bas shud 'gros kyis bskor lam la rgyud pa'i
NK014(pha)009:1432: te / 'khor mtshams / dgu pa stob 'chams ni /
NK014(pha)009:1434: zhes rkang g.yas phyir log ste rkang g.yon 'gro'i yongs phyogs su bzhi 'gros gsum nas /
NK014(pha)009:1435: gcig ces rkang g.yas g.yas su nem 'jog /
NK014(pha)009:1436: gnyis gnyis la rkang g.yas g.yon bskor gyi len nas
NK014(pha)009:1437: rkang pa g.yon pa dang g.yas pas rang phyogs su
NK014(pha)009:1439: rkang g.yas nang du phab pa'i sbir sbram gnyis kyi dzam len nas /
NK014(pha)009:1440: rkang g.yas sngon 'gro'i 'gro phyogs su bzhi 'gros gsum dang /
NK014(pha)009:1441: gcig ces rkang g.yon g.yon du nem 'jog sogs rkang pa ldog pas 'bebs bskor sngar ltar byas la /
NK014(pha)009:1442: g.yon nang phab kyi dzam len nas /
NK014(pha)009:1443: rkang g.yas sngon 'gros bzhi 'gros gsum dbus su phyin rjes sbir sbram gnyis la /
NK014(pha)009:1444: g.yas g.yon du lag gi stob pa'i stangs ka re byas la rol mo 'bebs pa ste /
NK014(pha)009:1445: de dag gi dkyil 'khor lha'i stangs stabs song ngo //
NK014(pha)009:1446: bcu gcig pa phur bu gdab pas bsrung ba ni /
NK014(pha)009:1447: slob dpon dbus nas shar du phyogs pa'i mdun du
NK014(pha)009:1448: mtshan nyid ji lta ba bzhin du 'du byas pa'i
NK014(pha)009:1450: mig la sogs pa'i h'u yig las 'od zer 'phros /
NK014(pha)009:1451: rdo rje sa gzhi'i ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla
NK014(pha)009:1452: re phyi rol bskal pa'i me dpung rab tu 'bar
NK014(pha)009:1453: ba'i dbus su b+h+r+aum las byung ba'i 'khor lo ser
NK014(pha)009:1454: po rtsibs brgyad la sogs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1455: rtsa rtse steng 'og tu phyogs shing rno ba'i dbal dang ldan pa /
NK014(pha)009:1456: lto ba chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa'i dbus bdag
NK014(pha)009:1457: nyid zhe sdang rdo rjer gnas pa'i thugs ka'i h'u
NK014(pha)009:1458: las ma bcu 'phros pa rtsibs nang so sor nyi
NK014(pha)009:1459: gdan bcur gyur / slar yang thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po 'phros /
NK014(pha)009:1460: phyogs bcu'i bgegs rnams bkug ste nyi gdan rnams kyi
NK014(pha)009:1461: steng du myos shing 'gyel stabs su 'khod par gyur
NK014(pha)009:1463: slar yang thugs ka nas khro bo bcu phyungs te
NK014(pha)009:1464: mdun du bkod pa'i phur bu rnams dang gnyis su
NK014(pha)009:1465: med par gyur pa ni stod khro bo'i gzugs can
NK014(pha)009:1466: smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pa can du gyur
NK014(pha)009:1467: par bsam la / slob dpon gyi tho ba phur bu bcu po re re nas thogs la /
NK014(pha)009:1468: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum gardza gardza h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)009:1469: ces sogs khro bo bcu'i sngags kyi mthar /
NK014(pha)009:1470: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK014(pha)009:1471: sarba dush+tana phata k+ai la ya k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam phata /
NK014(pha)009:1472: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra k+ai la ya /
NK014(pha)009:1473: badz+ra d+ha ra +aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK014(pha)009:1474: sarba big+h+n+aam k+aa ya w+aa k+aa tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)009:1476: khro bcu so so'i sngags rnams la /
NK014(pha)009:1477: steng dang phyogs kyi khro bo rnams badz+ra kro d+ha
NK014(pha)009:1478: la rkang g.yon btegs 'bebs kyi len nas drang por
NK014(pha)009:1479: btsugs pa la h+aum k+aa ra h+aum gardza gardza zhes
NK014(pha)009:1480: pa lta bu khro bo rang rang gi ming dang
NK014(pha)009:1481: las bye brag pa'i sngags rnams la rkang g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1482: phyogs su bskor / de bzhin du mtshams dang 'og
NK014(pha)009:1483: gi khro bo rnams rkang g.yas bteg len gyi drang
NK014(pha)009:1484: por btsugs pa la rkang g.yon gyis g.yas phyogs su
NK014(pha)009:1485: bskor zhing bcu ga'i mjug gi h+aum phata la rkang
NK014(pha)009:1487: 'chams pa gzhan rnams kyis kyang phur bu g.yon du
NK014(pha)009:1488: spos nas slob dpon dang mthun par mdun du gdengs
NK014(pha)009:1489: stabs / g+ha g+ha nas sarba dush+tana gyi bar la rkang lag g.yas pa phyir 'then zhing 'gying nas /
NK014(pha)009:1490: phata la rkang g.yon nang du phab ste slob dpon
NK014(pha)009:1491: gyis g.yas tho ba 'phyar zhing gzhan rnams kyis kyang
NK014(pha)009:1492: stangs ka bya / k+ai la ya nas h+aum h+aum
NK014(pha)009:1493: gyi bar 'gying stabs nas rkang g.yas zol gyis cung
NK014(pha)009:1494: zad bteg pa h+aum la nang du phab ste badz+ra
NK014(pha)009:1495: k+ai la ya zhes pa'i bar tho bas phur bu
NK014(pha)009:1496: stangs ka bya / brdung / badz+ra d+ha ra +aa
NK014(pha)009:1497: dz+ny+aa pa ya ti la rkang g.yon nang du phab
NK014(pha)009:1498: stangs ka bya / brdung / la brdung / sarba
NK014(pha)009:1499: big+h+n+aam nas k+ai la ya'i bar rkang g.yas nang du
NK014(pha)009:1500: stangs ka bya / brdung / la brdung / spo
NK014(pha)009:1501: zhing brdung / h+aum phata la g.yon spo zhing brdung
NK014(pha)009:1502: stangs ka bya / brdung / la brdung / spo
NK014(pha)009:1503: zhing brdung / ba ste / tshul de kho nas
NK014(pha)009:1504: phyogs kyi phur bu g.yas bskor dang mtshams kyi phur
NK014(pha)009:1505: stangs ka bya / brdung / la brdung / spo
NK014(pha)009:1506: zhing brdung / ba ste / bu g.yon bskor /
NK014(pha)009:1507: steng gi phur bu shar dang 'og gi phur bu
NK014(pha)009:1509: khro bo rnams phyogs bcu'i bgegs la phur bu'i tshul du btab pas /
NK014(pha)009:1510: de rnams kyis lus phug ste g.yo 'gul med cing 'od gsal bar gyur par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)009:1511: bcu gnyis pa rtag chad kyi mtha' bsal ba ni /
NK014(pha)009:1513: chig brdeg che bzhi bar mtshams rol 'thab dang bcas
NK014(pha)009:1514: par rkang g.yas bteg cing g.yon pa'i rting gsig gis
NK014(pha)009:1518: g.yon rnams su rim gyis phab cing gom chung gis do ra mnyam la /
NK014(pha)009:1519: g.yon bteg len nas bzhi brdungs kyis mchongs pad song don yangs pad skyur gtod nas /
NK014(pha)009:1520: rkang g.yas kho nas rwa btsal zhing gnyis gnyis zhes
NK014(pha)009:1521: par rkang g.yas g.yon 'degs 'bebs byas pa'i rdo rje
NK014(pha)009:1522: phyed 'gros tshar gsum gyis sgo gsum rdo rje gsum
NK014(pha)009:1523: gyi rang bzhin du dbyer mi phyed pa'i bsdu bya'i
NK014(pha)009:1525: bzhi 'gros kyis mtshan 'dzin gyi khong mdud gzhig phyir
NK014(pha)009:1526: sbrul nag 'khyil 'gros kyis chas 'jug khang par rim
NK014(pha)009:1527: gyis song ste rgyan chas rnams bkrol la rten dang
NK014(pha)009:1528: brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bsdus te mi dmigs pa thig
NK014(pha)009:1529: le'i dbyings su thim par bsam pas rtag mtha' bsal
NK014(pha)009:1530: zhing / slar yang rgyun chas la 'jug pa na
NK014(pha)009:1531: he ru ka'i skur skad cig gis langs te go
NK014(pha)009:1532: bgo lus bsrung bya bas chad mtha' bsal lo //
NK014(pha)009:1533: bcu gsum pa bsngo shis bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)009:1534: dge ba bsngo ba dang shis pa brjod pas mtha' rgyas su bya zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1535: de thams cad kyang sems dang ye shes rang snang
NK014(pha)009:1536: ba'i mtshan nyid tsam du shes pas skabs ji lta
NK014(pha)009:1537: ba'i cho ga'i khrigs rim gyi dkyus dang sbyar ro
NK014(pha)009:1538: // gal te dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i stangs stabs kyi
NK014(pha)009:1539: bkod pa sngar smos pa dag mi nus pas bsdus
NK014(pha)009:1541: bka' bsgos bgegs bskrad pa song rjes dpal chen po
NK014(pha)009:1542: khro bo bcu dang bcas pa'i stangs stabs bcu gcig
NK014(pha)009:1543: po byas la sngar bzhin phur bu gdab pas bsrung
NK014(pha)009:1544: ba tsam byas na'ang dgos don 'grub ste /
NK014(pha)009:1545: de ltar khro bo'i stang stabs kyis //
NK014(pha)009:1546: sngags dang ting 'dzin phyag rgyar bcas //
NK014(pha)009:1547: dkyil 'khor mtha' mar bskor ba yis //
NK014(pha)009:1548: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams brlag par byed //
NK014(pha)009:1551: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags par gsungs pa'i stangs stabs bcu gcig ste /
NK014(pha)009:1552: de yang phyag rgya ji ltar bca' ba'i tshig dang
NK014(pha)009:1553: bskul sngags la zur 'dra min 'ga' re snang yang
NK014(pha)009:1554: 'dir rgyud kyi rdo rje'i tshig kho na 'bri bar
NK014(pha)009:1555: bya ba las / thog mar gtso bo dpal chen po'i las bzhi'i phyag rgya ni /
NK014(pha)009:1556: lag pa thal sbyar gyen du sgrengs //
NK014(pha)009:1557: rkang gnyis mthil sbyar mthur du gzug /
NK014(pha)009:1558: tshig chen bzhi yang gzhig par bya //
NK014(pha)009:1559: mgo dang mtshan ma snying por brtag /
NK014(pha)009:1560: rdo rje rtse dgu rtse lnga dang //
NK014(pha)009:1561: bcu gcig tu yang rnam brtag ste //
NK014(pha)009:1563: phyag rgya yin zhes dpa' bos bshad //
NK014(pha)009:1564: ces gsungs pa'i bca' tshul ni /
NK014(pha)009:1566: sa blag snying po rtse gcig dang //
NK014(pha)009:1567: rtse lnga rtse dgu bcu gcig tu //
NK014(pha)009:1568: las rnams so so rab tu bsgom //
NK014(pha)009:1570: las kyi phyag rgya ni mgo bo rtse bcu gcig par bsam pa bca' ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:1571: gzhan sor mo g.yas g.yon bri bsnan gyis rtse lnga pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1573: bcu gcig pa ni zhi rgyas dbang drag gi rim pa bzhin no //
NK014(pha)009:1575: spro na sgeg mo'i snyems glu dang sbyar la /
NK014(pha)009:1576: rkang stabs gzhi bca' la lag stabs lag pa zhes par pad skor /
NK014(pha)009:1577: thal zhes par lag g.yas pus steng phab par sbyar la gdengs /
NK014(pha)009:1578: gyen la rkang g.yas brkyang dang rdor dril snying gar steng 'og tu sprad /
NK014(pha)009:1579: du sgrengs la spyi bor thal sbyor dang /
NK014(pha)009:1580: rkang gnyis mthil sbyar la rkang mthil gnyis sbyar te
NK014(pha)009:1581: rtse btsug pa mthur du gzug la pus mo cung
NK014(pha)009:1582: zad bcag nas zlum stabs bya ba ni zhi ba
NK014(pha)009:1584: tshig la ro stod cung zad g.yas su g.yom pa dzam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1585: chen bzhi la lag sngar nyid las rkang g.yas brkyang gis g.yas phyogs su gsigs 'gros gnyis /
NK014(pha)009:1586: yang la stod g.yon phyogs la g.yon pa'i dzam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1587: gzhig par la g.yon du gsigs 'gros gnyis byas nas /
NK014(pha)009:1589: mgo dang mtshan ma snying por brtag la bzhi pad mthar lag gnyis so sor gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:1590: rkang pa rang sa las lag gnyis rdo la cung
NK014(pha)009:1591: zad nang bskor gyis dzam nas rje la phyag rgya'i
NK014(pha)009:1592: rgyu thal sbyar rtse dgu la thal mo rting sprad
