NK014(pha)009:1593: nas gung gnyis rtse sprad pa dbus rwa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1594: sor mo gzhan rnams brkyang nas bskor ba rwa phra
NK014(pha)009:1595: men gyi tshul te dbang gi las rgya rtse dgu
NK014(pha)009:1596: pa'o // rtse lnga dang la de nyid la srin lag gnyis bsdoms /
NK014(pha)009:1597: mthe bong dang mathe'u chung so sor gshib nas bsgrengs /
NK014(pha)009:1598: mdzub mo gnyis gung mo'i rgyab tu sgreng ba ste rgyas pa'i las rgya rtse lnga pa'o //
NK014(pha)009:1599: de nas mgo bo dbus rwa dang g.yas g.yon gyi
NK014(pha)009:1600: lag sor bcu po dpung pa'i thad kar gdengs pa
NK014(pha)009:1601: rwa bcu'i dod de bcu zhes par g.yon dang gcig
NK014(pha)009:1602: la g.yas su thal mo bskor tshul byas pa ste
NK014(pha)009:1603: drag po'i las rgya bcu gcig pa'o //
NK014(pha)009:1604: tu yang la lag pad rnam brtag la lag g.yas pus steng ste la rdor gdengs /
NK014(pha)009:1605: 'di ni khrag 'thung chen po yi zhes par bzhi pad mthar lag sor gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:1606: phyag rgya yin zhes dpa' bos bshad ces lag pa
NK014(pha)009:1607: dang rkang pa bzhi g.yon dkrugs mthar g.yon brkyang zhing
NK014(pha)009:1608: lag rdo rje thugs ka dang dril bu dkur brten
NK014(pha)009:1610: badz+ra kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)009:1612: ces par rkang lag gi stabs rang sa las /
NK014(pha)009:1613: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)009:1614: phur gdab kyi phyogs kyi khro bo ltar g.yon du
NK014(pha)009:1615: bskor mthar rkang g.yon brkyang pa dang lag g.yon 'phyar
NK014(pha)009:1616: g.yas thugs kar sdigs mdzub bya zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1617: yang gar dbyangs kyi spros pa de tsam mi nus na /
NK014(pha)009:1618: phyag rgya bca' ba'i tshig dang bstun nas rgya bca'
NK014(pha)009:1619: zhing bskul sngags la bskor 'gying tsam byas kyang 'gal
NK014(pha)009:1620: ba med do // khro bo gzhan rnams ni gang
NK014(pha)009:1621: gi tshe so so'i tshigs bcad la rgya bca' zhing
NK014(pha)009:1622: mjug gi bskul sngags la phur gdab ltar steng dang
NK014(pha)009:1623: phyogs kyi khro bo g.yon dang /
NK014(pha)009:1624: mtshams dang 'og gi khro bo g.yas su bskor zhing
NK014(pha)009:1625: mjug tu phata la steng dang phyogs gtso bo ltar
NK014(pha)009:1626: dang / mtshams dang 'og de las ldog ste rkang g.yas brkyang ngo //
NK014(pha)009:1628: lag pa thal sbyar gyen du sgreng //
NK014(pha)009:1629: rkang pa phral nas brkyang bskum bya //
NK014(pha)009:1630: gom pa'i stabs kyis gar byed pa //
NK014(pha)009:1631: 'di ni h'u mdzad phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1632: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u gardza gardza h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1633: rkang pa rkang mgo g.yon gyis g.yas barla la la 'khyud //
NK014(pha)009:1634: lag pa gar stabs bskor nas kyang //
NK014(pha)009:1635: thal mo drag tu brdeb pa ni //
NK014(pha)009:1636: rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1637: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1638: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong gis //
NK014(pha)009:1639: mathe'u chung sen mo'i mthil du mnan //
NK014(pha)009:1640: gdengs pa'i stabs sor mo gsum kyis sgrengs pa yi //
NK014(pha)009:1641: dbyug pa sngon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1642: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1643: lag pa g.yas pa'i khu tshur ni //
NK014(pha)009:1644: brdeg pa'i stabs su gdengs pa dang //
NK014(pha)009:1645: g.yon pa dku la brten pa ni //
NK014(pha)009:1646: gshin rje 'joms pa'i phyag rgya yin /
NK014(pha)009:1647: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1648: lag pa g.yas pa'i thal mo ni //
NK014(pha)009:1649: brdeg pa'i stabs su gdengs ka dang //
NK014(pha)009:1650: g.yon pas 'dzin pa ltar byed pa //
NK014(pha)009:1651: mi g.yo mgon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1652: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1653: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba ni //
NK014(pha)009:1654: mdzub mo rgyab tu bsnol bar bya //
NK014(pha)009:1655: mthe bong gnyis kyang phral te sgrengs //
NK014(pha)009:1656: spyi bor bzhag pa g+r+ai wa'i rgya //
NK014(pha)009:1657: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai wa h+aum hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1658: rkang pa g.yas pa mthur du gzug /
NK014(pha)009:1659: lag pa gnyis po gyen du sgrengs //
NK014(pha)009:1660: g.yon gyi rkang pa 'phyar ba ni //
NK014(pha)009:1661: gzhan gyis mi thub phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1662: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u tish+tha tish+tha h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1663: lag pa g.yas g.yon dkur brten te //
NK014(pha)009:1664: rkang pa gshibs te mchong ba ni //
NK014(pha)009:1665: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya zhes //
NK014(pha)009:1666: dpa' bo chen pos yang dag bshad //
NK014(pha)009:1667: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da l+ai h'u tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1668: lag pas g.yas g.yon bsnol thugs kar ba dang //
NK014(pha)009:1669: rkang pa brkyang bskum byas pa ni //
NK014(pha)009:1670: khams gsum rnam rgyal phyag rgya zhes //
NK014(pha)009:1671: mgon po dpa' bos yang dag bshad //
NK014(pha)009:1672: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u b+hin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1673: rkang phral mthil ni thur du zug /
NK014(pha)009:1674: lag pa phral nas gar byed cing //
NK014(pha)009:1675: stabs su mchong bar byed pa ste //
NK014(pha)009:1676: 'di ni stobs chen phyag rgya yin //
NK014(pha)009:1677: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h'u s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK014(pha)009:1678: ces khro bo gang dang gang gi stangs stabs byas
NK014(pha)009:1679: pa de'i tshe de dang de'i sprul pa grangs med
NK014(pha)009:1682: slar 'dus pa las khro bo'i sprin gyis phyogs bcur gtams te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)009:1683: de nas sgrub pa'i zhag bdun pa lta bu'i tshogs mchod kyi stob pa dang sbrel ba'am /
NK014(pha)009:1684: gnas skabs gang yang rung bar rdzas kyi sgo nas
NK014(pha)009:1685: drag po'i phrin las la sbyor ba'i phyir dgra bgegs
NK014(pha)009:1687: chas 'jug khang par song la chas gos brlabs shing bgo ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:1688: phyi nas gser skyems bsngo ba rnams rtsa 'chams ltar byas rjes rten bca' ba /
NK014(pha)009:1692: pho nya 'gyed pa yan sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i sgrub thabs las byung ba ltar /
NK014(pha)009:1693: thugs rje 'dzin ging du mnga' gsol ba yod na dang /
NK014(pha)009:1694: med na mchod g.yog gis ling+ga bskyal la /
NK014(pha)009:1697: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad chos kyi 'byung
NK014(pha)009:1698: gnas gru gsum mthing nag 'byams klas la bskal pa'i
NK014(pha)009:1700: h'u ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK014(pha)009:1701: zhes brjod pas nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad
NK014(pha)009:1702: khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs par gyur
NK014(pha)009:1717: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)009:1718: zhes las la gzud pas lha tshogs rnams drag po'i las la rngam zhing khros par bsam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1720: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:1721: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1722: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1723: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1724: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1725: sprul pa yang sprul bka' sdod phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1726: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis ma rung
NK014(pha)009:1727: ba'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa thams
NK014(pha)009:1728: cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten la mchis par gyur
NK014(pha)009:1729: cig / n+ri yam dzah n+ri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah
NK014(pha)009:1730: tri yam dzah tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK014(pha)009:1731: hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis bstim pa tsam byas rjes
NK014(pha)009:1732: phyi rol nas spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra tsham
NK014(pha)009:1733: rngams dang bcas pas bskul te /
NK014(pha)009:1734: 'chams dpon gyis snyems pa dang bcas pas don te
NK014(pha)009:1735: sgo'i phyi mtshams nas 'gro phyogs su lus kyi g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1737: sbir sbram zhes gnyis brdung 'theng ma gnyis la 'gying
NK014(pha)009:1738: ba dang bcas pas g.yon g.yas kyis dzam blang ste
NK014(pha)009:1739: / bzhi brdung 'gros kyis rkang g.yon pa'i gsum thog nas yangs pad kyi 'go brtsam /
NK014(pha)009:1740: gcig gnyis zhes par dgag pad len /
NK014(pha)009:1741: gsum bzhi la lag g.yas phyir 'then te myang nas /
NK014(pha)009:1743: gsum bzhi la phur dar bsgyur /
NK014(pha)009:1744: yang gcig gnyis la b+han d+har phur rtse gtod /
NK014(pha)009:1745: gsum bzhi la lag g.yas g.yon par nang bskor gyis
NK014(pha)009:1746: phur dar steng du dor ba dang mnyam du rkang
NK014(pha)009:1747: g.yon g.yas nas 'degs 'bebs nas bzhi 'gros la zhugs
NK014(pha)009:1748: pa dang bstun gzhan rnams kyang gral phreng ba dang
NK014(pha)009:1749: mnyam pas rim par don te g.yon pa'i bzhi 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1753: gnyis ka dkur brten pa'i tshul gyis bzhi brdungs 'gros kho nas dor ma 'khor bar 'gro ste /
NK014(pha)009:1754: rdo rje lam 'gros zhes bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)009:1755: de las lag dkur gyi rnga gsum pa'i thog phata kyis bsgyur te yang pad brtsams nas /
NK014(pha)009:1756: dgag pad len sgyur gtod pa rnams sngar bzhin dang
NK014(pha)009:1757: rtsa 'chams kyi sna tshogs rdo rje'i mjug gi bzhi
NK014(pha)009:1758: brdung rol pa ji lta ba bzhin byas rjes chig
NK014(pha)009:1759: brdeg che gsum rol 'thab dang bcas pa chung gcig
NK014(pha)009:1760: la rkang g.yas g.yon re mos kyis do ra'i mdun
NK014(pha)009:1763: 'ong phyogs kyi zur rnams su 'bebs shing /
NK014(pha)009:1764: de bstun lag kyang rim bzhin gnyis ka gdengs pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1766: phyir bskor gyi mdun du gyen gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:1767: h'u rgya lta bus mdun du mnyam pa ste /
NK014(pha)009:1768: dpal chen po'i sgeg 'gros sam dga' ba yongs su bsgyur ba zhes bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)009:1769: de las phata kyis bsgyur te sbram sbram la yangs
NK014(pha)009:1770: pad kyis 'go brtsams nas sbir sbram tshan gsum gyi
NK014(pha)009:1771: re re la dgag skyur gtod gsum nas rtsa 'chams
NK014(pha)009:1772: ltar chig brdung rol pa byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1773: sbir zhes chig brdung che ba rol 'thab dang bcas
NK014(pha)009:1774: pa la lag gnyis phyir gdengs nas rkang g.yas 'gro
NK014(pha)009:1775: phyogs su bgrad stabs kyis 'degs 'bebs dang nang du
NK014(pha)009:1776: bskor 'gying nas sbram la lag mdun du mnyam zhing
NK014(pha)009:1777: rkang g.yon zur du brjid 'bebs las zlum stabs bya
NK014(pha)009:1779: de las phata kyis bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1780: pad brtsams dgag skyur gtod pas chig rol nas rnga chen bzhi la rkang g.yas lcags ri'i mdun dang /
NK014(pha)009:1783: g.yon rnams su 'degs 'bebs dang de bstun lag gnyis
NK014(pha)009:1784: kyang gsig rjes rnga chung gcig la rkang g.yon mdun
NK014(pha)009:1785: du bskor 'bebs kyis g.yon g.yas kyi dzam blangs nas
NK014(pha)009:1786: bzhi 'gros la 'jug ste stag mo'i rngams 'chams zhes
NK014(pha)009:1787: bya'o // de las phata kyis bsgyur te pad rtsams dgag skyur gtod pa nas /
NK014(pha)009:1788: sbram gcig nas gsum gyi bar rol pa byas rjes
NK014(pha)009:1789: bzhi par g.yas su 'phar ba bsigs kyi dzam len
NK014(pha)009:1791: rnga brel ba drug gi bar g.yon pa'i rting bsigs kyis chos bskor du bskor nas /
NK014(pha)009:1792: bdun la rkang g.yas phye dang /
NK014(pha)009:1793: brgyad la g.yon zur du phab /
NK014(pha)009:1794: dgu dgu zhes pa'i dzam la g.yon g.yas kyi dzam
NK014(pha)009:1795: blang nas bzhi 'gros la 'jug ste lce spyang gi
NK014(pha)009:1796: bsigs 'gros kyis bskor ba zhes bya'o //
NK014(pha)009:1797: de las phata kyis bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1798: sbir sbram tshan gnyis la mdun du dgag pad dang lag g.yas 'then brgyang /
NK014(pha)009:1799: sbram sbram la rkang g.yon 'degs 'bebs kyis g.yas su kha bskyur te /
NK014(pha)009:1800: sbir sbram tshan gsum la dgag pad skyur gtod byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1801: rnga thing chung bzhi'i bar la lag g.yon dkur brten
NK014(pha)009:1802: dang g.yas brkyangs pas g.yab cing phyir gom gsum nur
NK014(pha)009:1803: nas / bzhi brdungs drag po gcig la g.yas sdigs
NK014(pha)009:1804: mdzub ling+gara bsdigs pas rkang g.yas brkyang gis nang du
NK014(pha)009:1805: nas / bsigs 'gros gsum / de nas rnga chung
NK014(pha)009:1806: gnyis la rang sar bsdad nas che gnyis la rkang
NK014(pha)009:1807: g.yas 'degs 'bebs kyis g.yon phyogs su kha bsgyur nas
NK014(pha)009:1809: rnga thing chung bzhi la g.yon pas phyir g.yob pa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1810: che bzhi la g.yon brkyang gis nang du bsigs 'gros gsum nas chung gnyis la rang sa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1811: 'bring brdeg gnyis la g.yas su ldog g.yom gyis rol bsig rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1812: g.yon g.yas kyis dzam blangs nas bzhi 'gros la 'jug
NK014(pha)009:1813: ste spyang mo 'dur 'gros kyis g.yab cing 'chams zhes
NK014(pha)009:1814: bya'o // de las phata kyis bsgyur te sbir sbram
NK014(pha)009:1815: tshan gnyis la mdun du dgag pa dang g.yas 'then
NK014(pha)009:1816: bya'o // brgyang / sbram sbram la rkang g.yon gyis
NK014(pha)009:1817: g.yas su kha bsgyur te sbir sbram tshan gnyis la
NK014(pha)009:1819: de bzhin du mdun du rkang g.yas kyis bsgyur ba'i dgag pad 'then brgyangs dang /
NK014(pha)009:1820: rkang g.yon gyis g.yas su kha bsgyur te dgag pad skyur gtod byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1822: gnyis gnyis zhes 'ther brdung kho na las 'then bsrig rnams che rgyag dang /
NK014(pha)009:1824: gcig gcig la sdigs mdzub gnyis nang du ling+gara bsdig cing /
NK014(pha)009:1825: gnyis gnyis la rkang g.yas 'then nas g.yon lcags ris
NK014(pha)009:1826: la bsgyur cing sdigs mdzub gnyis phyir 'phyang nas gcig
NK014(pha)009:1828: gnyis gnyis la rkang g.yon 'degs 'debs dang g.yas lcags ris gnyis gcig gcig /
NK014(pha)009:1829: gnyis gnyis la sdigs mdzub nang bsdigs /
NK014(pha)009:1830: yang sdigs mdzub phyir 'phyar gyis gcig gcig la rang sa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1831: gnyis gnyis la pus mo g.yo btsug kyis tsog pur
NK014(pha)009:1832: lhan gyis 'dug nas g.yon g.yas su rol pa gnyis
NK014(pha)009:1833: re byas rjes har langs kyis lag g.yon dkur brten
NK014(pha)009:1835: rnga dgu brdungs kyi drug gi bar rting bsigs g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1836: du bskor nas bdun brgyad la lag g.yas phyir bskor
NK014(pha)009:1837: bas dgu la ling+ga sdigs mdzub gyen bstan gyis bsdigs
NK014(pha)009:1838: / bzhi brdeg chung brel phyed gnyis la rang sa dang /
NK014(pha)009:1839: gsum bzhi la rkang g.yas kyis g.yon du bsgyur te dgag pad 'then brgyangs /
NK014(pha)009:1840: g.yon gyis nang du ldog ste dgag pad 'then brgyangs /
NK014(pha)009:1841: g.yas kyis g.yon du ldog ste dgag pad skyur gtod byas rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1843: gnyis gnyis zhes rnga 'theng brdungs la sdigs mdzub nang du ling+gara bsdigs shing rkang g.yon 'then pa /
NK014(pha)009:1844: rkang g.yas lcags ris su bsgyur ba sogs g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)009:1845: go ldog pa ma gtogs sngar ji lta ba las
NK014(pha)009:1846: / lag g.yas 'phyar gyis dgu la ling+gara sdigs mdzub
NK014(pha)009:1847: gyen bstan gyis bsdigs nas bzhi brdungs chung brel phyed
NK014(pha)009:1848: gnyis la rang sar bsdad rjes /
NK014(pha)009:1849: phyed phyi mar g.yas su stod g.yom gyis ral bsigs
NK014(pha)009:1850: nas g.yon g.yas kyi dzam len te dred mo'i rgyug
NK014(pha)009:1851: 'gros kyis 'khyil zhing bsdigs pa zhes bya'o //
NK014(pha)009:1853: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK014(pha)009:1854: 'bar ba gtum chen rngam pa la //
NK014(pha)009:1855: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK014(pha)009:1856: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK014(pha)009:1857: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK014(pha)009:1858: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK014(pha)009:1859: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK014(pha)009:1860: rdul du byas nas tshogs la 'bul //
NK014(pha)009:1861: zhes pa la gdab kha'i rtsa dbyangs bcug ste 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1862: stabs tshig rkang re la bzhi 'gros tshar gnyis gnyis
NK014(pha)009:1863: las mi 'dra ba'i khyad par g.yon pa'i bzhi 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1864: kyi gsum bzhi zhes par g.yas su 'then te 'chams
NK014(pha)009:1865: pa tsam mo // de yang khams gsum sgrol ging
NK014(pha)009:1866: du mnga' gsol ba'i 'chams dpon gyis gdab phur thogs
NK014(pha)009:1867: pa tsam mo // la / e yi zhes par g.yas nas brtsams pa'i 'gros blangs te /
NK014(pha)009:1868: ji srid rkang pa bdun pa rdzogs pa'i bar dang /
NK014(pha)009:1869: brgyad pa'i rdul du zhes pa yan la 'jam 'gros
NK014(pha)009:1870: byas nas tshogs la 'bul zhes par rkang pa btegs
NK014(pha)009:1871: nas shugs cher bskyod cing dbyangs 'gros 'tshub pa dang
NK014(pha)009:1872: 'chams dpon nang du rim gyis zhugs nas rkang pa
NK014(pha)009:1873: tha mar ling+ga'i mdun du sleb par byas nas dbyangs
NK014(pha)009:1874: rdzogs pa'i ba'i ba'i la rkang g.yon btegs pa'i pad
NK014(pha)009:1875: brtsam nas bzung / nang du bsigs 'gros kyis 'gro
NK014(pha)009:1876: ba'i sar spyang mo 'dur 'gros kyis g.yas g.yon ji
NK014(pha)009:1877: lta ba bzhin bya ste rnga chung gnyis la rang
NK014(pha)009:1878: brtsam nas bzung / sar bsdad rjes / gsum bzhi la lag yangs pad dang /
NK014(pha)009:1879: rkang g.yas 'degs 'bebs kyis g.yon du bskor nas /
NK014(pha)009:1880: rkang g.yon btegs te gcig gnyis la rang sar 'gying /
NK014(pha)009:1881: gsum bzhi la yangs pad dang rkang g.yon gyis phyir
NK014(pha)009:1882: ldog ste g.yas btegs nas bzhi grangs gcig la de
NK014(pha)009:1883: khar 'gying nas / sbir sbram la g.yon pa'i rting
NK014(pha)009:1884: bsig gis 'phar te rkang g.yas su phab cing g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1886: de bzhin du nang du phyir phyogs su rol bsigs kyis dzam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1887: rab 'bebs dang bstun nang du g.yas sngon 'gro'i gom gnyis nur nas tsog pur bsdad /
NK014(pha)009:1888: ling+ga'i gnas gsum du phur bu gdab /
NK014(pha)009:1889: de'i tshe slob dpon dpal chen po'i nga rgyal la
NK014(pha)009:1890: gnas pas ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba'i thabs kyis
NK014(pha)009:1891: mdzad spyod tshe khrus kyi dgongs pa la bzhag go
NK014(pha)009:1892: // de nas sgrol gri thogs te rol pa gnyis
NK014(pha)009:1893: blang rjes har langs kyis rkang g.yas lcags ris su
NK014(pha)009:1894: bkod nas rkang pa mi btegs pa ma gtogs gzhan
NK014(pha)009:1895: sngar bzhin lce spyang gi bsigs 'gros ji lta bas
NK014(pha)009:1896: bskor bas mjug gi g.yon g.yas kyi dzam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1898: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK014(pha)009:1900: thal ba bzhin du brlag byas nas //
NK014(pha)009:1901: drag po'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)009:1902: ces par dbyangs 'gros gnyis ka sngar ltar la bsdad
NK014(pha)009:1903: nas sgrol gris dmigs yul pho mo'i khyad par gyis
NK014(pha)009:1904: rkang pa g.yas g.yon gang rigs nas brtsams te dum
NK014(pha)009:1905: bur gtub cing / snga phyi gnyis ka'i gdab sngags
NK014(pha)009:1906: so sor bshad pa bzhin nam bsdus pa la dga'
NK014(pha)009:1907: na gnyis ka la ru lu'i rjes su /
NK014(pha)009:1908: sarba dush+tana m+aa ra ya h'u phata //
NK014(pha)009:1909: ces spel bas kyang rung ngo //
NK014(pha)009:1910: de nas langs te lce spyang gi bsigs 'gros lta bus bskor ba'i tshe /
NK014(pha)009:1911: 'chams dpon gyis grangs bdun gyi bar brgyang 'gros kyis
NK014(pha)009:1912: gral du zhugs nas g.yon g.yas kyi dzam rjes phata
NK014(pha)009:1913: kyis bsgyur te / lnga drug gi bar dgu skor rlung 'tshubs ma spyi ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1914: bdun la rkang g.yon mi 'bebs par /
NK014(pha)009:1916: dgu dgu zhes par rkang g.yas g.yon 'degs 'jog dang
NK014(pha)009:1917: bstun lag stabs kyi khyad par dgu bskor tshar bzhi'i
NK014(pha)009:1920: gsum par gnyis ka brgyangs pa /
NK014(pha)009:1921: bzhi par dkur brten pa rnams te //
NK014(pha)009:1922: de dag la pho nya'i bsgral 'chams zhes bya'o //
NK014(pha)009:1923: de nas ye shes stob gang gi chas su zhugs pa yod na dang /
NK014(pha)009:1924: med na las rdor gyis ling ro zhing lpags kyi
NK014(pha)009:1925: snod du spungs la rog dang bcas pas btegs nas
NK014(pha)009:1927: 'chams dpon gyis phata kyis bsgyur te bzhi 'gros blangs
NK014(pha)009:1928: nas g.yas pa'i gsum bzhi'i 'gros thog yangs pad bya
NK014(pha)009:1929: ste mdun du lag gyen bstan gyis bsnyab nas /
NK014(pha)009:1931: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK014(pha)009:1932: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer brdal ba ltar //
NK014(pha)009:1933: zhes pa la stob dbyangs che ba 'gros dang bcas pa bya ste /
NK014(pha)009:1934: bee d+aur sngon yan la rkang g.yon brkyang dang lag gnyis mdun du gyen bstan mnyam /
NK014(pha)009:1935: po'i la rkang g.yon mdun dang g.yas kyis 'gros su
NK014(pha)009:1936: cung zad spo zhing lag gnyis g.yas 'phyar gyis stob
NK014(pha)009:1937: pa'i stangs ka / rin 'as la rkang g.yon btegs 'bebs dang lag gnyis gzhol /
NK014(pha)009:1938: chen la rting bsigs dang lag gnyis stob tshul /
NK014(pha)009:1939: ri la rkang g.yas g.yon bskor gyis 'gro phyogs 'bebs pa dang g.yon stob /
NK014(pha)009:1940: rab la'ang rkang g.yas btegs 'bebs dang g.yon stob /
NK014(pha)009:1941: la zhes par rkang g.yas mdun du zol po dang lag gyen mnyam /
NK014(pha)009:1942: wa la g.yon drud cing dbus stob /
NK014(pha)009:1943: ba'i la rkang g.yas cung zad spos te /
NK014(pha)009:1944: ba'i nyi ya ma zhes par g.yon pa'i rting bsigs kyis g.yas g.yon du ldog ste /
NK014(pha)009:1945: stong la rkang g.yas g.yas 'then dang lag gnyis g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1946: su stob pa'i stong ga gi 'od zer brdal la
NK014(pha)009:1947: zhes pa yan sngar ltar las /
NK014(pha)009:1948: ba zhes par rkang g.yas cung zad btegs 'bab dang g.yon drud de dbus su stob /
NK014(pha)009:1949: ltar ra la rkang g.yon 'gro phyogs su spo zhing g.yas phyir drud /
NK014(pha)009:1950: 'a wa'i la rkang g.yon bteg len nas rol 'gros la 'jug /
NK014(pha)009:1951: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK014(pha)009:1952: dpal ldan gzi byin 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:1953: zhes pa'ang dbyangs 'gros gnyis ka snga ma nyid ldab /
NK014(pha)009:1955: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yi //
NK014(pha)009:1956: 'jigs byed rngams stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK014(pha)009:1957: za byed bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba ste //
NK014(pha)009:1958: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK014(pha)009:1959: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK014(pha)009:1960: khams gsum za bar chas pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK014(pha)009:1961: nyi zla rab tu 'bar ba'i sdang mig gis //
NK014(pha)009:1962: bdun dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)009:1963: zhes pa'i shwa lo ka gnyis po la lha'i rkang ston stob pa'i rtsa dbyangs bcug ste /
NK014(pha)009:1964: 'od phung stug po zhes pa'i bar rkang g.yon brkyang dang lag mnyam ste 'dug /
NK014(pha)009:1965: sprin ltar la stod g.yom dang bcas pa rkang g.yas g.yas su spos nas /
NK014(pha)009:1966: 'khrigs pa la rkang g.yon drud cing lag gnyis g.yas stob /
NK014(pha)009:1967: la 'a zhes par rkang g.yon btegs nas yi ya dor stabs su phabs /
NK014(pha)009:1968: 'a wa'i 'e ya rnams la rang sar 'gying /
NK014(pha)009:1969: 'jigs byed rngam stabs kyis rkang pa gcig por rkang lag ldog pas g.yon stob ste /
NK014(pha)009:1970: tshul des g.yas g.yon res mos kyis shwa lo ka
NK014(pha)009:1971: dang po song ba'i mjug gi 'e ya zhes par
NK014(pha)009:1972: rkang g.yas g.yas su spos pa'i len nas yong phyogs
NK014(pha)009:1973: su rkang g.yon nas brtsams pa'i bzhi 'gros la bcug
NK014(pha)009:1974: pa'i g.yon 'gros kyis gsum bzhi zhes par yangs pad
NK014(pha)009:1975: mthar lag gyen bstan mnyam nas /
NK014(pha)009:1976: mi bzad mche ba sogs la dbyangs 'gros gzhan sngar
NK014(pha)009:1977: ltar las thog mar g.yon stob dang mjug tu g.yas
NK014(pha)009:1978: nas brtsam pa'i bzhi 'gros kyis 'gro phyogs la bskor
NK014(pha)009:1980: dug gsum stob pa rgyas pa ni /
NK014(pha)009:1981: 'byung po'i sha ni zan las zhim //
NK014(pha)009:1982: gti mug mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)009:1983: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //

NK014(pha)009:1986: 'dod chags mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)009:1987: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)009:1988: gsung gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:1989: 'byung po'i rus pa mar las zhim //
NK014(pha)009:1990: zhe sdang mchod pa bla na med //
NK014(pha)009:1991: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)009:1992: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)009:1993: zhes shwa lo ka gsum po la re re la g.yas g.yon dbus rnams su 'gro zhing /
NK014(pha)009:1995: dug gsum dgra bgegs bsgral ba yi //
NK014(pha)009:1996: sha khrag rus gsum sogs kyi shwa lo ka gcig
NK014(pha)009:1997: por dug gsum stob kyi rtsa dbyangs rtsa gdangs su
NK014(pha)009:1998: grags pas bkab ste h'u la rkang g.yon btegs pa'i
NK014(pha)009:1999: len nas / tshig rkang gi 'og thams cad la
NK014(pha)009:2000: rkang g.yas 'degs pa phyogs so sor ldog tshul shes
NK014(pha)009:2001: len nas / par byas la / lag gnyis stob
NK014(pha)009:2002: pa'i stangs ka g.yas g.yon khyer zhing rkang pa g.yas
NK014(pha)009:2003: g.yon re mos kyis 'degs 'bebs byed la 'jol 'gros
NK014(pha)009:2004: su grags pas tshig rkang dang po la yong phyogs
NK014(pha)009:2005: len nas / par byas la / / gnyis par 'gro phyogs /
NK014(pha)009:2007: bzhi par dbus su 'gro ba ste /
NK014(pha)009:2008: de dag la rdo rje srin po'i bstab 'chams zhes bya'o //
NK014(pha)009:2009: de nas dbyangs mjug gi gsol la zhes par rkang g.yon btegs pas len nas phata kyis bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)009:2010: rdo rje phyed 'gros tshar gsum dang sbrul nag 'khyil
NK014(pha)009:2011: 'gros kyis chas 'jug khang par rim gyis 'gro tshul
NK014(pha)009:2013: 'dir rdol thabs su smra ba kha cig /
NK014(pha)009:2014: rtsa 'chams dang grub 'chams 'di phur pa'i 'chams yin
NK014(pha)009:2015: pas sgyu 'phrul sogs la sbyor ba ni rigs pa
NK014(pha)009:2016: ma yin zhes ga zha byed pa ni rang rang
NK014(pha)009:2017: gi mthong rgya dang rnam dpyod chung ba ston pa
NK014(pha)009:2018: tsam ste / rgyu mtshan sgyu 'phrul khrag 'thung gi
NK014(pha)009:2019: 'chams kyi phyag bzhes zur che chung nas rim par
NK014(pha)009:2021: chos rje bsod rgyan pa'i bka' bzhin shes rab snang
NK014(pha)009:2022: bas lam gyi dka' spyad bzod par byas nas 'dar
NK014(pha)009:2023: ston gyi drung du phyin te tshul 'di la mkhas
NK014(pha)009:2024: par sbyangs te / rjes chos rje e wam rim
NK014(pha)009:2025: par rnams la bslabs nas phur pa la'ang sgyu 'phrul
NK014(pha)009:2026: khro bo'i rtsa 'chams kho na'i phyag len tshar gnyis
NK014(pha)009:2027: mdzad nas slad kyis phur 'chams su bsgyur ba yin
NK014(pha)009:2029: bdag gis bla ma'i gnang ba thob //
NK014(pha)009:2030: bka' bzhin bgrod daka'i gnas su phyin //
NK014(pha)009:2031: dgongs bzhin slob dpon dam pa rnyed //
NK014(pha)009:2032: tshul bzhin 'di don brtson pas sbyang //
NK014(pha)009:2033: bzhed bzhin lus bsgyur ji bzhin lon //
NK014(pha)009:2034: chos kyi rje la gzigs par phul //
NK014(pha)009:2035: ji bzhin yin zhes rjes su gnang //
NK014(pha)009:2036: bka' 'khor dang bcas rnams la bslab //
NK014(pha)009:2037: 'di la phyag len lan gnyis mdzad //
NK014(pha)009:2039: keng rus gzhal yas khang rnams bsnan //
NK014(pha)009:2040: koo ri seng ha'i 'chams tshul rnams //
NK014(pha)009:2041: phyag brnyan phra men phyag rgyar bsgyur //
NK014(pha)009:2042: 'di la phyag len mang du mdzad //
NK014(pha)009:2043: ces gsungs pa ltar yin pas 'dir sgyu 'phrul khro
NK014(pha)009:2044: bo la sbyar ba ni rang nor rang gis spyod
NK014(pha)009:2045: pa'i phyir shin tu'ang rigs shing 'thad pa lags so
NK014(pha)009:2046: // des na 'di yi lag khrid kyi brgyud pa'ang /
NK014(pha)009:2047: rgyal po dzahns mkhas pa mi gsum la brgyud de bod kyi lo chen rma gnyags /
NK014(pha)009:2057: dpa' 'dar rnam gnyis dang 'bro ston la bstan pa las /
NK014(pha)009:2059: chos slong ba bsod nams dpal /
NK014(pha)009:2064: khos sngags 'chang ngag dbang grags pa /
NK014(pha)009:2065: mi yi dbang po bi dza ya /
NK014(pha)009:2067: mkhas pa blo bzang rab brtan te de nyid kyi
NK014(pha)009:2068: drung du kho bo cag gis kyang rje bla ma'i
NK014(pha)009:2069: bka' stsal thod du bcings nas o rgyan smin grol
NK014(pha)009:2070: gling gi gtsug lag khang chen po 'di nyid du
NK014(pha)009:2071: tshul bzhin du sbyangs pa las cung zad shes par
NK014(pha)009:2073: gzhan yang seng rgya mkhar ba dang /
NK014(pha)009:2075: zur yang dben pa'i dam can gyi 'chams rnams mthong
NK014(pha)009:2076: zhing 'chams tshul gyi gnad cung zad rigs par byas
NK014(pha)009:2077: te / yi ge 'di yang 'dar gyi yig rnying
NK014(pha)009:2078: dang lus 'gyur snang ba'i nang gi khro bo nga
NK014(pha)009:2079: brgyad kyi phyag chen bsgyur tshul sogs la gtso bor
NK014(pha)009:2080: te / brten cing / se dang rog gi yi
NK014(pha)009:2081: ge sogs la'ang legs par brtags te khung dag cing
NK014(pha)009:2082: go bde bar spel ba yin no //
NK014(pha)009:2083: dpal ldan khrag 'thung sgyu 'phrul rdo rje'i gar //
NK014(pha)009:2084: kun bzang rnam par rtsen pa'i rol pa yi //
NK014(pha)009:2085: gsal bar mtshon 'di myos btsun gar thig pa //
NK014(pha)009:2086: d+har+m+aa sh+r+ais brjed byang nyid du spel //
NK014(pha)009:2087: 'di las rab dkar bsod nams gang thob des //
NK014(pha)009:2088: rdo rje lus kyi spyod pa rmad byung la //
NK014(pha)009:2089: brten nas 'gro kun las dang dngos grub cher //
NK014(pha)009:2090: bdag gir skal ba bzang po myong gyur cig //
